. Note that the course fee does not include the certification exam fee.&nbsp;</p>' WHERE value_id=9445;
UPDATE catalog_product_entity_text SET value='<p>Elevate your graphic design skills with our Illustrator CC Essential Training at Tertiary Courses. This comprehensive program is tailored to impart expertise in a range of techniques, from managing artboards and layers, to creating intricate compound paths and shapes. Dive into the core tools and functionalities, such as scaling, rotating, and adding vibrant color fills, while harnessing the power of the Appearance panel to apply multiple strokes and fills.</p>\n<p>Hone precision drawing skills using the renowned Pen tool, and bring life to your designs with the versatile brush tools. Delve deep into the art of typography, seamlessly place and embed high-resolution images, and ensure your masterpieces are ready for print or digital display. Whether you''re a budding designer or seeking advanced proficiency, this course offers a robust understanding, positioning you at the forefront of the digital design landscape.</p>\n<h2>Certificate</h2>\n<p>All participants will receive a Certificate of Completion from Tertiary Courses after achieved at least 75% attendance.</p>' WHERE value_id=9495;
