Certification</h2>\n<p>At the end of the course, participants will sit for the ITIL Foundation exam in Singapore . Those who pass scoring at least 65% will be awarded ITIL Foundation Certificate from AXELOS and the test will be conducted through PEOPLECERT..</p>\n<h2>Funding and Grant Applications</h2>\n<p>No funding is available for this course</p>\n</div>\n' WHERE value_id=140806;
