UPDATE catalog_product_entity_text SET value='<h2><strong><span style="color: #ff0000;">This course is currently not available</span></strong></h2>\n<p>ITIL V3 Foundations Boot Camp is a 2-day intensive program by an experienced professional&nbsp;who has an actual experience in implementing best ITIL best practices and designed to help&nbsp;participants achieve ITIL Foundation certification</p>\n<h2>Why ITIL?</h2>\n<p>IT organizations are faced with a rapidly evolving where standardization on procedures is&nbsp;becoming a major requirement and a critical success factor. Information Technology&nbsp;Infrastructure Library (ITIL), is the preeminent framework for managing IT service delivery&nbsp;around the world. ITIL defines a service lifecycle model that prescribes specific processes&nbsp;and activities during the design, development, delivery and support of IT services.&nbsp;ITIL&rsquo;s body of knowledge represent the consensus derived from over a decade of work and&nbsp;experience by thousands of IT professionals world-wide, earning for it the status as de facto&nbsp;world standard for IT best practices. More and more organizations are therefore mandating&nbsp;ITIL certification for their staff and contractors.</p>\n<h2>Benefits</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Career growth for potential salary increase and/or promotion</li>\n<li>Complete &ldquo;turnkey&rdquo; comprehensive ITIL V3 training program to help gain ITIL&nbsp;foundation certification</li>\n<li>Gain practical ITIL skills you will immediately use on the job</li>\n<li>Increase your effectiveness on the job in days</li>\n<li>Actionable learning, case studies, classroom discussions and Q&amp;A sessions</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>Who Should Attend</h2>\n<p><br />ITIL V3 Foundations boot camp is an introductory-level course intended for IT professionals&nbsp;responsible for developing, supporting, and operating application-based IT services (e.g.,&nbsp;messaging) and infrastructure-based IT services (e.g., network services).</p>\n<h2>Certification</h2>\n<p>At the end of the course, participants will sit for the ITIL Foundation exam in Singapore . Those who pass scoring at least 65% will be awarded ITIL Foundation Certificate from AXELOS and the test will be conducted through PEOPLECERT..</p>\n<h2>Funding and Grant Applications</h2>\n<p>No funding is available for this course</p>\n</div>\n' WHERE value_id=142594;
UPDATE catalog_product_entity_text SET value='<p>Embark on an enlightening journey into the realm of Tableau, a leading tool for data visualization and business intelligence. This Full Tableau Training is meticulously designed to bridge the gap between data potential and actionable insights. Learn the intricacies of Tableau Worksheets, harness the dynamism of Tableau Dashboard &amp; Story, and delve deep into data organization techniques such as Filters, Groups, and Sets.</p>\n<p>From connecting to diverse data sources to mastering advanced techniques like Field Calculation, Parameters, and Level of Expressions, this course ensures you&rsquo;re well-equipped. Moreover, elevate your data stories with Map Visualization and understand the nuances of Data Join and Pivot. With hands-on exercises and expert-led content, realize the complete capabilities of Tableau, turning raw data into compelling visual narratives.</p>\n<h2>Certificate</h2>\n<p>All participants will receive a Certificate of Completion from Tertiary Courses after achieved at least 75% attendance.</p>\n<h2>Funding and Grant</h2>\n<p><span style="font-size: medium; color: #ff0000;"><a href="https://hrdcorp.gov.my/employer-guidelines/" title="HRDF claimable-HRD Corp claimable" target="_blank"><span style="color: #ff0000;">HRD Corp Claimable Course for Employers Registered with HRD Corp</span></a></span></p>\n<p><img alt="HRDF claimable" height="100" src="media/wysiwyg/Logo_HRD_Corp_Claimable_programme-1.jpg" title="HRDF claimable-HRD Corp claimable" width="100" /></p>\n' WHERE value_id=142693;
UPDATE catalog_product_entity_text SET value='<p>Elevate your digital design journey with our Photoshop CC Essential Training at Tertiary Courses. This meticulously curated program dives deep into the foundational aspects of Photoshop, providing keen insights into image resizing, cropping, and the nuanced world of layers. Whether reshaping visuals through transformations or understanding the benefits of Smart Objects, we ensure you acquire the skills to make your digital visions come to life.</p>\n<p>Master the art of layer masks, empowering you to craft intricate designs seamlessly. The course will guide you through making accurate selections, optimizing the image editing process, and infusing your projects with adjustment layers for that perfect finish. Step into a world where your digital design dreams and Photoshop''s vast capabilities intersect, and leave with a renewed confidence in your graphic editing prowess.</p>\n<h2>Certificate</h2>\n<p>All participants will receive a Certificate of Completion from Tertiary Courses after achieved at least 75% attendance.</p>\n\n<h2>Funding and Grant Applications</h2>\n<p><span style="font-size: medium; color: #ff0000;"><a href="https://hrdcorp.gov.my/employer-guidelines/" title="HRDF claimable-HRD Corp claimable" target="_blank"><span style="color: #ff0000;">HRD Corp SBL KHAS Claimable for Employers Registered with HRD Corp</span></a></span></p>\n<p><img alt="HRDF claimable" height="100" src="media/wysiwyg/Logo_HRD_Corp_Claimable_programme-1.jpg" title="HRDF claimable-HRD Corp claimable" width="100" /></p>\n' WHERE value_id=142711;
UPDATE catalog_product_entity_text SET value='<p>Elevate your graphic design skills with our Illustrator CC Essential Training at Tertiary Courses. This comprehensive program is tailored to impart expertise in a range of techniques, from managing artboards and layers, to creating intricate compound paths and shapes. Dive into the core tools and functionalities, such as scaling, rotating, and adding vibrant color fills, while harnessing the power of the Appearance panel to apply multiple strokes and fills.</p>\n<p>Hone precision drawing skills using the renowned Pen tool, and bring life to your designs with the versatile brush tools. Delve deep into the art of typography, seamlessly place and embed high-resolution images, and ensure your masterpieces are ready for print or digital display. Whether you''re a budding designer or seeking advanced proficiency, this course offers a robust understanding, positioning you at the forefront of the digital design landscape.</p>\n<h2>Certificate</h2>\n<p>All participants will receive a Certificate of Completion from Tertiary Courses after achieved at least 75% attendance.</p>\n\n<h2>Funding and Grant Applications</h2>\n<p><span style="font-size: medium; color: #ff0000;"><a href="https://hrdcorp.gov.my/employer-guidelines/" title="HRDF claimable-HRD Corp claimable" target="_blank"><span style="color: #ff0000;">HRD Corp SBL KHAS Claimable for Employers Registered with HRD Corp</span></a></span></p>\n<p><img alt="HRDF claimable" height="100" src="media/wysiwyg/Logo_HRD_Corp_Claimable_programme-1.jpg" title="HRDF claimable-HRD Corp claimable" width="100" /></p>\n' WHERE value_id=142720;
UPDATE catalog_product_entity_text SET value='<p>Unlock the full potential of cloud-based accounting with our QuickBooks Online Plus Training at Tertiary Courses. Designed for both beginners and seasoned accountants, this course takes you through the intricate features of the renowned software. Learn the nuances of setting up accounts, managing customers and vendors, and delve deep into products, services, and billable expenses. Whether it''s time tracking, handling refunds, or automating transactions, this training ensures you''re adept in every facet of QuickBooks Online.</p>\n<p>Efficiently manage your financial tasks, from paying bills, creating invoices to setting up online banking accounts, and generating insightful reports. With expert guidance on sales tax and the automation of recurring transactions, you''ll be well-equipped to streamline your financial processes, saving both time and effort. Immerse in this transformative training, ensuring that your financial management, whether for personal or business purposes, reaches new heights of precision and efficiency.</p>\n<h2>Certificate</h2>\n<p>All participants will receive a Certificate of Completion from Tertiary Courses after achieved at least 75% attendance.</p>\n\n<h2>Funding and Grant Applications</h2>\n<p><span style="font-size: medium; color: #ff0000;"><a href="https://hrdcorp.gov.my/employer-guidelines/" title="HRDF claimable-HRD Corp claimable" target="_blank"><span style="color: #ff0000;">HRD Corp SBL KHAS Claimable for Employers Registered with HRD Corp</span></a></span></p>\n<p><img alt="HRDF claimable" height="100" src="media/wysiwyg/Logo_HRD_Corp_Claimable_programme-1.jpg" title="HRDF claimable-HRD Corp claimable" width="100" /></p>' WHERE value_id=142767;
UPDATE catalog_product_entity_text SET value='<p>Dive into the world of Neo4j and get a comprehensive understanding of its fundamentals. From basic graph theory and graph structures to Cypher fundamentals, our course covers every essential aspect. Learn how Neo4j implements index-free-adjacency and understand the intricacies of reading and writing data to Neo4j. Embrace the power of graph data modeling, understanding nodes, relationships, and the significance of graph data models.</p>\n<p>Expand your knowledge with intermediate topics like Neo4j Database Administration and data importing techniques. Grasp the nuances of Neo4j Graph Data Science, discover the synergy between Neo4j and Python, and prepare effectively for the Neo4j Certified Professional Exam. Enrich your skillset and become a proficient user of Neo4j with Tertiary Courses.</p>\n\n<h2>Certificate</h2>\n<p>All participants will receive a Certificate of Completion from Tertiary Courses after achieved at least 75% attendance.</p>\n\n<p><iframe frameborder="0" height="315" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/jCzQPr-BBhk?rel=0&amp;controls=0&amp;showinfo=0" width="400"></iframe></p>\n\n<h2>Certification Exam</h2>\n<p>Once you are prepared for the exam, you can register for the certification&nbsp;<span style="text-decoration: underline;"><a href="https://graphacademy.neo4j.com/courses/neo4j-certification/" title="Neo4j Certification" target="_blank">here</a></span>.&nbsp;We are Authorised Pearson Vue Testing Center. You can take the certification exam at our test center. Note that the course fee does not include the certification exam fee.</p>\n\n<h2>Funding and Grant</h2>\n<p><span style="font-size: medium; color: #ff0000;"><a href="https://hrdcorp.gov.my/employer-guidelines/" title="HRDF claimable-HRD Corp claimable" target="_blank"><span style="color: #ff0000;">HRD Corp Claimable Course for Employers Registered with HRD Corp</span></a></span></p>\n<p><img alt="HRDF claimable" height="100" src="media/wysiwyg/Logo_HRD_Corp_Claimable_programme-1.jpg" title="HRDF claimable-HRD Corp claimable" width="100" /></p>\n' WHERE value_id=143046;
UPDATE catalog_product_entity_text SET value='<p>Unearth the intricacies of Adobe Premiere Pro CC, an industry-standard tool that promises to elevate your video editing capabilities. Our meticulous training begins with a fast-track approach to editing in Premiere Pro, guiding you through the foundational steps of setting up projects, sequences, and mastering the art of importing and organizing media. Learn to discern and select the finest takes from your clips and delve into the nuances of various editing techniques, including insert, overwrite, and replace edits. Seamlessly manage your clips with skills in trimming, splitting, moving, and deletion.</p>\n<p>Broaden your editing horizon as you explore the power of dynamic linking with other Creative Cloud applications. Enhance your auditory experience with pristine audio editing, mixing, and voice-over recording. Dive deeper into the world of video embellishments as you apply transitions, effects, and filters. Master the techniques of changing clip speed, perfecting color correction, crafting compelling titles, and employing multicam editing. Upon culmination, you will be adept at exporting your refined projects, ensuring they resonate with your desired audience. With Tertiary Courses, embrace the professional realm of Adobe Premiere Pro CC.</p>\n<h2>Certificate</h2>\n<p>All participants will receive a Certificate of Completion from Tertiary Courses after achieved at least 75% attendance.</p>\n\n<h2>Funding and Grant</h2>\n<p><span style="font-size: medium; color: #ff0000;"><a href="https://hrdcorp.gov.my/employer-guidelines/" title="HRDF claimable-HRD Corp claimable" target="_blank"><span style="color: #ff0000;">HRD Corp Claimable Course for Employers Registered with HRD Corp</span></a></span></p>\n<p><img alt="HRDF claimable" height="100" src="media/wysiwyg/Logo_HRD_Corp_Claimable_programme-1.jpg" title="HRDF claimable-HRD Corp claimable" width="100" /></p>\n' WHERE value_id=143138;
UPDATE catalog_product_entity_text SET value='<p>Unlock the vast potentials of Adobe InDesign CC with our tailored Essential Training. Designed for both beginners and professionals, this course offers a comprehensive journey from the basics, like getting acquainted with the user interface, to advanced design techniques. Within just 30 minutes, embark on a hands-on experience, setting up new documents, and effortlessly placing graphics, ensuring every project reflects impeccable design standards.</p>\n<p>Delve deeper into the nuances of color swatches, layers, and object transformation to bring your design visions to life. Learn the art of creating engaging multidocument books, interactive PDFs, and exporting to EPUB, ensuring each document stands out. With a special focus on document proofing using the Preflight panel and effective printing and exporting strategies, this training ensures you''re equipped with the skills to navigate InDesign CC efficiently, making every design project a masterpiece.</p>\n<h2>Certificate</h2>\n<p>All participants will receive a Certificate of Completion from Tertiary Courses after achieved at least 75% attendance.</p>' WHERE value_id=144003;
UPDATE catalog_product_entity_text SET value='<p>Unearth the power of Adobe''s After Effects CC with our detailed Essential Training. From novices looking to grasp the basics to seasoned professionals aiming to polish their skills, this course offers insights into the world of advanced video editing. Participants will be introduced to fundamental video terminology, enabling a clear understanding of the intricate facets of the editing landscape. The journey further delves into creating compelling compositions, mastering the art of using layers, masks, blend modes, and understanding the pivotal role of track mattes.</p>\n<p>With a focus on real-world applications, attendees will gain hands-on experience in building complex visual objects with Pre-compose, explore the ray-traced 3D renderer''s capabilities, and create enthralling 3D projects from Illustrator files. The course also sheds light on refining scenes through optimal lighting, animating captivating type on paths, utilizing Keylight for pristine green-screen footage, and the meticulous craft of rotoscoping. By the course''s culmination, learners will be well-equipped to create visually arresting video projects, setting them apart in the dynamic world of video editing and production.</p>\n<h2>Certificate</h2>\n<p>All participants will receive a Certificate of Completion from Tertiary Courses after achieved at least 75% attendance.</p>\n\n<h2>Funding and Grant</h2>\n<p><span style="font-size: medium; color: #ff0000;"><a href="https://hrdcorp.gov.my/employer-guidelines/" title="HRDF claimable-HRD Corp claimable" target="_blank"><span style="color: #ff0000;">HRD Corp Claimable Course for Employers Registered with HRD Corp</span></a></span></p>\n<p><img alt="HRDF claimable" height="100" src="media/wysiwyg/Logo_HRD_Corp_Claimable_programme-1.jpg" title="HRDF claimable-HRD Corp claimable" width="100" /></p>' WHERE value_id=144121;
UPDATE catalog_product_entity_text SET value='<p>Dive into the world of UI/UX design with our specialized Adobe XD Training. As the realm of digital design continuously evolves, it becomes crucial for professionals to stay updated with the latest tools and techniques. Adobe XD, a pioneer in the UI/UX design landscape, offers designers an integrated platform to craft, animate, and bring their visions to life. This course is meticulously curated to ensure participants gain a deep understanding of XD''s multifaceted features, making it an essential toolkit for any designer''s repertoire.</p>\n<p>Our training commences by introducing attendees to the intuitive XD interface, emphasizing seamless navigation techniques. Participants will explore the integration of prominent design tools like Photoshop, Illustrator, and Sketch with XD, amplifying their design capabilities. By harnessing the Repeat Grid feature, designers can effortlessly replicate elements, saving invaluable time. The course further delves into the realm of animations, teaching users how to add dynamic elements to their designs. Additionally, the innovative voice interactions feature of XD will be explored, paving the way for futuristic design solutions. The training culminates by guiding participants through the exporting process, ensuring designs are ready for any platform or medium. By the end of the sessions, participants will be well-versed in using Adobe XD, elevating their UI/UX design game manifold.</p>\n<h2>Certificate</h2>\n<p>All participants will receive a Certificate of Completion from Tertiary Courses after achieved at least 75% attendance.</p>\n\n<h2>Funding and Grant</h2>\n<p><span style="font-size: medium; color: #ff0000;"><a href="https://hrdcorp.gov.my/employer-guidelines/" title="HRDF claimable-HRD Corp claimable" target="_blank"><span style="color: #ff0000;">HRD Corp Claimable Course for Employers Registered with HRD Corp</span></a></span></p>\n<p><img alt="HRDF claimable" height="100" src="media/wysiwyg/Logo_HRD_Corp_Claimable_programme-1.jpg" title="HRDF claimable-HRD Corp claimable" width="100" /></p>' WHERE value_id=144129;
UPDATE catalog_product_entity_text SET value='<p>Immerse yourself in the transformative power of Kubernetes with our WSQ Certified Kubernetes Administrator (CKA) Exam Prep course. This course is meticulously designed to imbue learners with a strong foundational knowledge and practical skills necessary for developing a Kubernetes architectural proof of concept. The journey through this course will enable learners to identify the technical and practical requirements in a Kubernetes setup and subsequently develop a solution architecture within Kubernetes. As learners delve deeper, they will also prepare a technical blueprint for a Kubernetes-based solution focusing on crucial aspects like security and storage, ensuring a comprehensive understanding of deploying and managing applications within a Kubernetes environment.</p>\n<p>Transitioning to real-world application, this course emphasizes on demonstrating a Kubernetes solution for a specific business problem, thereby allowing learners to apply their acquired knowledge in practical scenarios. Additionally, the course covers the implementation of regular monitoring of the Kubernetes system and performing necessary troubleshooting, which are essential skills for maintaining a robust and efficient Kubernetes environment. Through a blend of theoretical learning and practical exercises, learners will not only be well-prepared for the Certified Kubernetes Administrator exam but also be empowered with the ability to leverage Kubernetes for solving complex business problems and significantly contribute to their organization''s technological advancements.</p>\n<h2>Learning Outcomes</h2>\n<p>By end of the course, learners should be able to:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>LO1: Develop a Kubernetes architectural proof of concept.</li>\n<li>LO2:&nbsp;Identify the technical and practical requirements in a Kubernetes setup.</li>\n<li>LO3:&nbsp;Develop a solution architecture within Kubernetes.</li>\n<li>LO4:&nbsp;Prepare a technical blueprint for a Kubernetes-based solution for security and storage.</li>\n<li>LO5:&nbsp;Demonstrate Kubernetes solution for a specific business problem.</li>\n<li>LO6:&nbsp;Implement regular monitoring of the Kubernetes system and perform necessary troubleshooting.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>Course Brochure</h2>\n<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><a href="https://www.tertiarycourses.com.sg/wsq-certified-kubernetes-administrator-cka-exam-prep-synchronous-e-learning.html" title="WSQ - Certified Kubernetes Administrator (CKA) Exam Prep (Synchronous e-Learning) Brochure" target="_blank">Download WSQ - Certified Kubernetes Administrator (CKA) Exam Prep (Synchronous e-Learning) Brochure</a></span></p>\n<h2>Skills Framework</h2>\n<p>This course follows the guideline of&nbsp;<strong><span lang="EN">Solution Architecture ICT-DES-4006-1.1&nbsp;</span></strong><span></span>under ICT Skills Framework</p>\n<h2>Certificate</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><strong>Certificate of Completion from Tertiary Infotech</strong> - Upon meeting at least 75% attendance and passing the assessment(s), participants will receive a Certificate of Completion from Tertiary Infotech.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><strong>OpenCerts from SkillsFuture Singapore</strong> - After passing the assessment(s) and achieving at least 75% attendance, participants will receive a OpenCert (aka Statement of Achievement) from SkillsFuture Singapore, certifying that they have achieved the Competency Standard(s) in the above Skills Framework.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>Certification Exam at Pearson Vue</h2>\n<p>Once you are prepared for the exam, you can register for the certification&nbsp;<span style="text-decoration: underline;"><a href="https://training.linuxfoundation.org/certification-catalog/" title="Linux Certification" target="_blank">here</a></span>.We are Authorised Pearson Vue Testing Center. You can take the certification exam at our test center. Note that the course fee does not include the certification exam fee.</p>\n<div style=" width: 100%; padding: 10px; border-radius: 25px;">\n<h2>WSQ Funding</h2>\n<p>WSQ funding is only applicable to Singaporeans and PR. Subject to eligibility, the funding support is subjected to funding caps.</p>\n<table border="1" style="width: 100%;">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td colspan="5" style="text-align: center;"><strong></strong><strong></strong><strong><span>Effective for courses starting from 1 Jan 2024</span></strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td rowspan="2" style="text-align: center;"><strong>Full Fee</strong></td>\n<td rowspan="2" style="text-align: center;"><strong>GST</strong></td>\n<td colspan="3" style="text-align: center;"><strong>Nett Fee after Funding (Incl. GST)</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style="text-align: center;"><span><strong>Baseline</strong></span></td>\n<td style="text-align: center;"><strong>MCES / SME</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style="text-align: center;">$2,000.00</td>\n<td style="text-align: center;">$180.00</td>\n<td style="text-align: center;">$1,180.00</td>\n<td style="text-align: center;">$780.00</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p>Baseline: Singaporean/PR age 21 and above<br />MCES(Mid-Career Enhanced Subsidy): S''porean age 40 &amp; above</p>\n<p>Upon registration, we will advise further on how to tap on the WSQ Training Subsidy.</p>\n<hr />\n<p>You can pay the nett fee (a<span>fter the WSQ training subsidy)&nbsp;</span>by the following :</p>\n<h3>SkillsFuture Enterprise Credit (SFEC)</h3>\n<p>Eligible Singapore-registered companies can tap on $10000 SFEC to cover out-of-pocket expenses.<a href="https://skillsfuture.gobusiness.gov.sg/course-directory/courses/TGS-2023039342" target="_blank"><span style="color: #ff0000; text-decoration-line: underline;">Click here to submit SkillsFuture Enterprise Credit</span></a></p>\n<h3>SkillsFuture Credit (SFC)</h3>\n<p>Eligible Singapore Citizens can use their SFC to offset course fee payable after funding but the $4,000 Additional SFC (Mid-Career Support) cannot be used. <a href="https://www.myskillsfuture.gov.sg/content/portal/en/training-exchange/course-directory/course-detail.html?courseReferenceNumber=TGS-2023039343" title="SkillsFuture Credit" target="_blank"><span style="color: #ff0000; text-decoration-line: underline;">Click here for SkillsFuture Credit submission</span></a></p>\n<h3>UTAP</h3>\n<p>Eligible NTUC members can apply for 50% of the unfunded fee from UTAP, capped up to $250/year and for members aged 40 and above, capped up to $500/year. <a href="https://www.ntuc.org.sg/wps/portal/up2/home/eserviceslanding?id=6bc1ca2c-ce81-4acb-a28f-c0be586e185f" target="_blank"><span style="color: #ff0000; text-decoration-line: underline;">Click here to submit UTAP</span></a></p>\n<h3>PSEA</h3>\n<p>Eligible Singapore Citizens can use their PSEA funds to offset course fee payable after funding.</p>\nTo check for Post-Secondary Education Account (PSEA) eligibility for this course, <a href="https://www.myskillsfuture.gov.sg/content/portal/en/training-exchange/course-directory/course-detail.html?courseReferenceNumber=TGS-2023039343" title="SkillsFuture Credit" target="_blank"><span style="color: #ff0000; text-decoration-line: underline;">Visit SkillsFuture (course code: TGS-2023039343) </span></a>\n<ul>\n<li>Scroll down to &ldquo;Keyword Tags&rdquo; to verify for PSEA eligibility.</li>\n<li>If there is &ldquo;PSEA&rdquo; under keyword tags, the course is eligible for PSEA.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Once you are eligible for PSEA, please download and fill up the <a href="https://www.moe.gov.sg/-/media/files/financial-matters/psea-ad-hoc-withdrawal-form.pdf" title="PSEA Withdrawal Form" target="_blank"><span style="text-decoration: underline; color: #ff0000;">PSEA Withdrawal Form</span></a> and email to us.&nbsp;</p>\n</div>' WHERE value_id=144429;
UPDATE catalog_product_entity_text SET value='<p>Embark on a transformative journey of technical prowess with our Certified Kubernetes Administrator (CKA) Exam Prep course. This meticulously designed course aims at equipping learners with the requisite knowledge and practical skills essential for mastering Kubernetes orchestration. Delving into the core functionalities and advanced features of Kubernetes, this course lays a solid foundation for managing and scaling containerized applications with ease and precision. The comprehensive curriculum encapsulates the essential Kubernetes concepts, security best practices, networking policies, and various other pivotal aspects, aligning with the course highlights to provide a well-rounded learning experience.</p>\n<p>Transitioning to the realms of professional expertise, this course facilitates a thorough understanding of Kubernetes orchestration, empowering learners to manage complex Kubernetes clusters proficiently. Through a blend of theoretical insights and hands-on exercises, learners will gain a profound understanding of deploying, managing, and scaling applications in a Kubernetes environment. Additionally, the course prepares learners for the Certified Kubernetes Administrator exam, providing them with the confidence and knowledge required to excel. The rigorous training and practical exposure provided through this course are instrumental in not only preparing learners for the CKA exam but also in fostering a robust understanding of Kubernetes orchestration, thus paving the way for a successful and fulfilling career in the burgeoning field of container orchestration and Kubernetes administration.</p>\n<h2>Certificate</h2>\n<p>All participants will receive a Certificate of Completion from Tertiary Courses after achieved at least 75% attendance.</p>\n\n<h2>Certification Exam at Pearson Vue</h2>\n<p>Once you are prepared for the exam, you can register for the certification&nbsp;<span style="text-decoration: underline;"><a href="https://training.linuxfoundation.org/certification-catalog/" title="Linux Certification" target="_blank">here</a></span>.We are Authorised Pearson Vue Testing Center. You can take the certification exam at our test center. Note that the course fee does not include the certification exam fee.</p>\n\n<h2>Funding and Grant</h2>\n<p><span style="font-size: medium; color: #ff0000;"><a href="http://www.hrdf.com.my/wps/portal/PSMB/MainEN/Schemes/HRDF/" title="HRDF claimable" target="_blank"><span style="color: #ff0000;">HRDF SBL Claimable for Employers Registered with HRDF</span></a></span></p>\n<p><img alt="HRDF claimable" height="84" src="media/wysiwyg/14054931_1763340620617768_4715474791535353517_n.jpg" title="HRDF claimable" width="64" /></p>' WHERE value_id=144473;
UPDATE catalog_product_entity_text SET value='<p><span>Unlock the power of Excel in the domain of trading and investment with this comprehensive training. Delve into foundational and advanced strategies including the Moving Average Crossover, Volume Weight Average Pricing (VWAP), and the Relative Strength Indicator (RSI). Complement these with a deep understanding of key metrics like Expected Return, Beta, and Volatility, setting the stage for informed and data-driven financial decisions. <br /><br />Furthermore, this course illuminates the intricacies of the Capital Asset Pricing Model, a cornerstone in modern financial theory. Whether you''re a budding trader or an investment professional, the integration of Excel with these critical strategies ensures a robust approach to the financial markets, optimizing your potential for success.</span></p>\n<h2>Certificate</h2>\n<p>All participants will receive a Certificate of Completion from Tertiary Courses after achieved at least 75% attendance.</p>\n<h2>Funding and Grant</h2>\n<p><span style="font-size: medium; color: #ff0000;"><a href="https://hrdcorp.gov.my/employer-guidelines/" title="HRDF claimable-HRD Corp claimable" target="_blank"><span style="color: #ff0000;">HRD Corp Claimable Course for Employers Registered with HRD Corp</span></a></span></p>\n<p><img alt="HRDF claimable" height="100" src="media/wysiwyg/Logo_HRD_Corp_Claimable_programme-1.jpg" title="HRDF claimable-HRD Corp claimable" width="100" /></p>' WHERE value_id=146089;
UPDATE catalog_product_entity_text SET value='<p>Dive deep into the world of C# programming within Unity software with our Unity Certified User Programmer Exam Prep. This course is meticulously designed to cover the essentials of creating interactivity in games, apps, and other immersive experiences. You will learn the ins and outs of Unity software and C# programming, ensuring you are well-prepared to take on the certification exam.</p>\n<p>With the exam objectives aligned with the current industry standards set by professionals and educators, our course guarantees that you receive the most relevant and up-to-date knowledge. We understand the importance of hands-on experience, and that''s why we recommend individuals to have at least 150 hours of Unity software use and training before obtaining this certification. Our course is not just about passing the exam; it''s about empowering you with the skills and knowledge needed to excel in your career. So, gear up and get ready to unlock new opportunities with our Unity Certified User Programmer Exam Prep.</p>\n\n<h2>Certificate</h2>\n<p>All participants will receive a Certificate of Completion from Tertiary Courses after achieved at least 75% attendance.</p>\n\n<h2>Certification Exam at Pearson Vue</h2>\n<p>Once you are prepared for the exam, you can register for the certification <span style="text-decoration: underline;"><a href="https://home.pearsonvue.com/unity/" title="Unity Certification" target="_blank">here</a></span>. We are Authorised Pearson Vue Testing Center. You can take the certification exam at our test center. Note that the course fee does not include the certification exam fee.</p>\n\n<h2>Funding and Grant</h2>\n<p><span style="font-size: medium; color: #ff0000;"><a href="https://hrdcorp.gov.my/employer-guidelines/" title="HRDF claimable-HRD Corp claimable" target="_blank"><span style="color: #ff0000;">HRD Corp Claimable Course for Employers Registered with HRD Corp</span></a></span></p>\n<p><img alt="HRDF claimable" height="100" src="media/wysiwyg/Logo_HRD_Corp_Claimable_programme-1.jpg" title="HRDF claimable-HRD Corp claimable" width="100" /></p>\n\n' WHERE value_id=151921;
UPDATE catalog_product_entity_text SET value='<p>Embark on a journey to mastering the Google Cloud Platform with our Google Associate Cloud Engineer Certification Exam Prep course. This comprehensive course is meticulously designed to equip you with the knowledge and skills needed to excel in the Google Associate Cloud Engineer Certification Exam, ensuring you are well-prepared to tackle the challenges of the exam and achieve certification success.</p>\n<p>Our course covers all the essential topics and provides practical insights to help you understand the intricacies of the Google Cloud Platform. With expert instructors and a curriculum tailored to the exam''s requirements, you will gain a deep understanding of the platform, enhancing your cloud skills and opening up new career opportunities. Enroll now and take the first step towards becoming a certified Google Associate Cloud Engineer.</p>\n<h2>Certificate</h2>\n<p>All participants will receive a Certificate of Completion from Tertiary Courses after achieved at least 75% attendance.</p>\n<h2>Register for Google Cloud Certification</h2>\n<p>Once you are prepared for the exam, you can register for the certification <span style="text-decoration: underline;"><a href="https://cloud.google.com/learn/certification?hl=en" title="Google Cloud Certification" target="_blank">here</a></span>.&nbsp;Note that the course fee does not include the certification exam fee.</p>\n<h2>Funding and Grant</h2>\n<p><span style="font-size: medium; color: #ff0000;"><a href="https://hrdcorp.gov.my/employer-guidelines/" title="HRDF claimable-HRD Corp claimable" target="_blank"><span style="color: #ff0000;">HRD Corp Claimable Course for Employers Registered with HRD Corp</span></a></span></p>\n<p><img alt="HRDF claimable" height="100" src="media/wysiwyg/Logo_HRD_Corp_Claimable_programme-1.jpg" title="HRDF claimable-HRD Corp claimable" width="100" /></p>' WHERE value_id=151983;
UPDATE catalog_product_entity_text SET value='<p>Dive deep into the world of cloud architecture with our Google Professional Cloud Architect Certification Exam Prep course. This meticulously crafted course is designed to provide you with the essential knowledge and skills required to excel in the Google Professional Cloud Architect Certification Exam. Our expert instructors will guide you through the complexities of the Google Cloud Platform, ensuring you are well-prepared to tackle the challenges of the exam and achieve certification success.</p>\n<p>Our course covers a comprehensive range of topics, providing you with a thorough understanding of cloud architecture and the Google Cloud Platform. You will gain practical insights and hands-on experience, enhancing your cloud skills and opening up new career opportunities. Enroll now and take the first step towards becoming a certified Google Professional Cloud Architect and elevating your career to new heights</p>\n<h2>Certificate</h2>\n<p>All participants will receive a Certificate of Completion from Tertiary Courses after achieved at least 75% attendance.</p>\n<h2>Register for Google Cloud Certification</h2>\n<p>Once you are prepared for the exam, you can register for the certification <span style="text-decoration: underline;"><a href="https://cloud.google.com/learn/certification?hl=en" title="Google Cloud Certification" target="_blank">here</a></span>.&nbsp;Note that the course fee does not include the certification exam fee.</p>\n<h2>Funding and Grant</h2>\n<p><span style="font-size: medium; color: #ff0000;"><a href="https://hrdcorp.gov.my/employer-guidelines/" title="HRDF claimable-HRD Corp claimable" target="_blank"><span style="color: #ff0000;">HRD Corp Claimable Course for Employers Registered with HRD Corp</span></a></span></p>\n<p><img alt="HRDF claimable" height="100" src="media/wysiwyg/Logo_HRD_Corp_Claimable_programme-1.jpg" title="HRDF claimable-HRD Corp claimable" width="100" /></p>' WHERE value_id=151999;
UPDATE catalog_product_entity_text SET value='<p>Unlock the full potential of cloud database technology with our comprehensive Google Professional Cloud Database Engineer course. This program offers an in-depth journey through the intricacies of designing, building, and maintaining databases on the Google Cloud Platform (GCP). Aimed at database professionals looking to leverage Google Cloud&rsquo;s powerful database services, this course will prepare you for the official Google certification with a strong emphasis on practical skills for real-world applications. Participants will delve into key topics such as cloud database architectures, storage options, and the dynamics of managing scalable and reliable data solutions that support enterprise operations.</p>\n<p>Our expert-led training is focused not only on passing the exam but also on ensuring that you can apply your knowledge immediately, with insights on integrating GCP databases within the Shopee ecosystem. By the end of this course, you will be adept at implementing, configuring, and troubleshooting GCP&rsquo;s database services, and you&rsquo;ll be ready to step into a role that requires advanced knowledge of cloud-based database solutions. Whether you are a seasoned IT professional or an aspiring cloud specialist, this course is your stepping stone to becoming a sought-after Google Professional Cloud Database Engineer, capable of transforming business data strategies into scalable successes.</p>\n<h2>Certificate</h2>\n<p>All participants will receive a Certificate of Completion from Tertiary Courses after achieved at least 75% attendance.</p>\n<h2>Register for Google Cloud Certification</h2>\n<p>Once you are prepared for the exam, you can register for the certification <span style="text-decoration: underline;"><a href="https://cloud.google.com/learn/certification?hl=en" title="Google Cloud Certification" target="_blank">here</a></span>.&nbsp;Note that the course fee does not include the certification exam fee.</p>\n<h2>Funding and Grant</h2>\n<p><span style="font-size: medium; color: #ff0000;"><a href="https://hrdcorp.gov.my/employer-guidelines/" title="HRDF claimable-HRD Corp claimable" target="_blank"><span style="color: #ff0000;">HRD Corp Claimable Course for Employers Registered with HRD Corp</span></a></span></p>\n<p><img alt="HRDF claimable" height="100" src="media/wysiwyg/Logo_HRD_Corp_Claimable_programme-1.jpg" title="HRDF claimable-HRD Corp claimable" width="100" /></p>' WHERE value_id=152371;
UPDATE catalog_product_entity_text SET value='<p>Dive into the profound capabilities of Machine Learning on the Google Cloud Platform with Tertiary Courses. Our in-depth curriculum sheds light on the myriad of hosting options available, be it Serverless, container-based, or via virtual machines, ensuring that you''re equipped to make informed decisions tailored to your specific needs. Grasp the essence of enabling GCP''s ML AIs and hone your skills in preparing data through Cloud Dataflow and Dataprep, pivotal for any robust ML pipeline.</p>\n<p>As we advance, delve into the intriguing world of modeling predictions for diverse media including images, video, text-to-speech, and cloud translation. Our hands-on approach ensures you''re adept at employing AutoML for streamlined ML tasks. We further delve into intricate machine learning and deep learning modules, wrapping up with a comprehensive understanding of modern ML architectures. This course is an indispensable asset for those enthusiastic about harnessing the full potential of machine learning on GCP.</p>\n<h2>Certificate</h2>\n<p>All participants will receive a Certificate of Completion from Tertiary Courses after achieved at least 75% attendance.</p>\n<h2>Register for Google Cloud Certification</h2>\n<p>Once you are prepared for the exam, you can register for the certification <span style="text-decoration: underline;"><a href="https://cloud.google.com/learn/certification?hl=en" title="Google Cloud Certification" target="_blank">here</a></span>.&nbsp;Note that the course fee does not include the certification exam fee.</p>\n<h2>Funding and Grant</h2>\n<p><span style="font-size: medium; color: #ff0000;"><a href="https://hrdcorp.gov.my/employer-guidelines/" title="HRDF claimable-HRD Corp claimable" target="_blank"><span style="color: #ff0000;">HRD Corp Claimable Course for Employers Registered with HRD Corp</span></a></span></p>\n<p><img alt="HRDF claimable" height="100" src="media/wysiwyg/Logo_HRD_Corp_Claimable_programme-1.jpg" title="HRDF claimable-HRD Corp claimable" width="100" /></p>' WHERE value_id=152476;
UPDATE catalog_product_entity_text SET value='<p>Embark on a journey to become a certified Unity Programmer with our comprehensive exam preparation course. This Unity Certified User (Programmer) course is meticulously designed to equip you with the expertise and confidence to pass the certification exam. Delve into the essentials of Unity''s development environment, mastering the fundamentals of scripting, animation, UI, game logic, and more. You''ll learn to troubleshoot common programming challenges, optimize game performance, and implement critical game design patterns.</p>\n<p>As you progress, practical assignments and mock tests will solidify your knowledge and test your skills in a simulated exam environment. Our industry-experienced instructors provide personalized feedback and insights to ensure you''re fully prepared for the exam. By the end of this course, you''ll not only be ready to ace the Unity Certified User Programmer Exam but also to embark on creating your own compelling games with professional proficiency.</p>\n<h2>Learning Outcomes</h2>\n<p>By end of the course, learners should be able to:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>LO1: Analyze gaming trends and prepare technical briefs aligning with state-of-the-art technology.</li>\n<li>LO2:&nbsp;Develop 2D game using Unity coding standards to meet the game''s technical requirements</li>\n<li>LO3:&nbsp;Develop 3D game prototypes using Unity with programming teams to meet the game''s technical goals.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>Course Brochure</h2>\n<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><a href="https://drive.google.com/file/d/1zZJW9yjcYCQxOj3hhjlWb-yu6MWcUxPk/view?usp=sharing" title="WSQ - Unity Certified User: Programmer Training Brochure" target="_blank">Download WSQ - Unity Certified User: Programmer Training Brochure</a></span></p>\n<h2>Skills Framework</h2>\n<p>This course follows the guideline of&nbsp;<strong><span>Game Technical Design MED-GDP-4003-1.1</span></strong><span></span><strong><span lang="EN">&nbsp;</span></strong><span></span><strong>&nbsp;</strong>under Media Skills Framework</p>\n<h2>Certification Exam at Pearson Vue</h2>\n<p>Once you are prepared for the exam, you can register for the certification&nbsp;<span style="text-decoration: underline;"><a href="https://home.pearsonvue.com/unity/" title="Unity Certification" target="_blank">here</a></span>. We are Authorised Pearson Vue Testing Center. You can take the certification exam at our test center. Note that the course fee does not include the certification exam fee.</p>\n<h2>Certification</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><strong>Certificate of Completion from Tertiary Infotech</strong> - Upon meeting at least 75% attendance and passing the assessment(s), participants will receive a Certificate of Completion from Tertiary Infotech.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><strong>OpenCerts from SkillsFuture Singapore</strong> - After passing the assessment(s) and achieving at least 75% attendance, participants will receive a OpenCert (aka Statement of Achievement) from SkillsFuture Singapore, certifying that they have achieved the Competency Standard(s) in the above Skills Framework.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<div style=" width: 100%; padding: 10px; border-radius: 25px;">\n<h2>WSQ Funding</h2>\n<p>WSQ funding is only applicable to Singaporeans and PR. Subject to eligibility, the funding support is subjected to funding caps.</p>\n<table border="1" style="width: 100%;">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td colspan="5" style="text-align: center;"><strong></strong><strong></strong><strong><span>Effective for courses starting from 1 Jan 2024</span></strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td rowspan="2" style="text-align: center;"><strong>Full Fee</strong></td>\n<td rowspan="2" style="text-align: center;"><strong>GST</strong></td>\n<td colspan="3" style="text-align: center;"><strong>Nett Fee after Funding (Incl. GST)</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style="text-align: center;"><span><strong>Baseline</strong></span></td>\n<td style="text-align: center;"><strong>MCES / SME</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style="text-align: center;">$1,600</td>\n<td style="text-align: center;">$144.00</td>\n<td style="text-align: center;">$944.00</td>\n<td style="text-align: center;">$624.00</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p>Baseline: Singaporean/PR age 21 and above<br />MCES(Mid-Career Enhanced Subsidy): S''porean age 40 &amp; above</p>\n<p>Upon registration, we will advise further on how to tap on the WSQ Training Subsidy.</p>\n<hr />\n<p>You can pay the nett fee (a<span>fter the WSQ training subsidy)&nbsp;</span>by the following :</p>\n<h3>SkillsFuture Enterprise Credit (SFEC)</h3>\n<p>Eligible Singapore-registered companies can tap on $10000 SFEC to cover out-of-pocket expenses.<a href="https://skillsfuture.gobusiness.gov.sg/course-directory/courses/TGS-2023040473" target="_blank"><span style="color: #ff0000; text-decoration-line: underline;">Click here to submit SkillsFuture Enterprise Credit</span></a></p>\n<h3>SkillsFuture Credit (SFC)</h3>\n<p>Eligible Singapore Citizens can use their SFC to offset course fee payable after funding but the $4,000 Additional SFC (Mid-Career Support) cannot be used. <a href="https://www.myskillsfuture.gov.sg/content/portal/en/training-exchange/course-directory/course-detail.html?courseReferenceNumber=TGS-2023040473" title="SkillsFuture Credit" target="_blank"><span style="color: #ff0000; text-decoration-line: underline;">Click here for SkillsFuture Credit submission</span></a></p>\n<h3>UTAP</h3>\n<p>Eligible NTUC members can apply for 50% of the unfunded fee from UTAP, capped up to $250/year and for members aged 40 and above, capped up to $500/year. <a href="https://www.ntuc.org.sg/wps/portal/up2/home/eserviceslanding?id=6bc1ca2c-ce81-4acb-a28f-c0be586e185f" target="_blank"><span style="color: #ff0000; text-decoration-line: underline;">Click here to submit UTAP</span></a></p>\n<p><span style="color: #333300;">Once you are eligible for PSEA, please download and fill up the <a href="https://www.moe.gov.sg/-/media/files/financial-matters/psea-ad-hoc-withdrawal-form.pdf" title="PSEA Withdrawal Form" target="_blank"><span style="text-decoration: underline; color: #ff0000;">PSEA Withdrawal Form</span></a>&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p><span style="color: #333300;">and email to us.&nbsp;</span></p>\n</div>' WHERE value_id=152507;
UPDATE catalog_product_entity_text SET value='<p>Embark on a journey to become a Google Professional Cloud Security Engineer with our comprehensive certification prep course. This course is meticulously designed for IT professionals aiming to deepen their expertise in cloud security on the Google Cloud Platform (GCP). You''ll gain in-depth knowledge of GCP''s core services, security best practices, and the latest strategies in securing cloud environments. Our curriculum covers critical aspects of cloud security, including identity and access management, data protection, and network security, providing you with the skills needed to design and implement secure infrastructure on GCP.</p>\n<p>Our expert instructors, equipped with real-world experience, will guide you through interactive sessions, practical exercises, and up-to-date course materials. The course is structured to not only prepare you for the Google Professional Cloud Security Engineer certification exam but also to enhance your practical skills for immediate application in your current or future roles. Whether you''re an IT security specialist, a cloud engineer, or an aspiring security professional, this course is your stepping stone to achieving certification and excelling in the realm of cloud security. Enroll now to secure your spot and advance your career in this rapidly evolving field.</p>\n<h2>Certificate</h2>\n<p>All participants will receive a Certificate of Completion from Tertiary Courses and official Autodesk Certificate of Completion after achieved at least 75% attendance.</p>\n\n<h2>Register for Google Cloud Certification</h2>\n<p>Once you are prepared for the exam, you can register for the certification <span style="text-decoration: underline;"><a href="https://cloud.google.com/learn/certification?hl=en" title="Google Cloud Certification" target="_blank">here</a></span>.&nbsp;Note that the course fee does not include the certification exam fee.</p>\n\n<h2>Funding and Grant</h2>\n<p><span style="font-size: medium; color: #ff0000;"><a href="https://hrdcorp.gov.my/employer-guidelines/" title="HRDF claimable-HRD Corp claimable" target="_blank"><span style="color: #ff0000;">HRD Corp Claimable Course for Employers Registered with HRD Corp</span></a></span></p>\n<p><img alt="HRDF claimable" height="100" src="media/wysiwyg/Logo_HRD_Corp_Claimable_programme-1.jpg" title="HRDF claimable-HRD Corp claimable" width="100" /></p>' WHERE value_id=155881;
UPDATE catalog_product_entity_text SET value='<p>Embark on a path to becoming a Google Professional Cloud Network Engineer with our dedicated certification prep course. This training is strategically designed for network professionals aiming to deepen their understanding of cloud-based networking on Google Cloud Platform (GCP). You''ll explore the intricacies of designing, planning, and implementing secure and scalable network architectures using GCP services. Our curriculum delves into critical aspects like network security, hybrid cloud configurations, and optimizing network performance, equipping you with the skills required to effectively manage and troubleshoot GCP networks.</p>\n<p>As part of this course, you will engage in practical, hands-on learning experiences that bring theoretical concepts to life. Guided by seasoned instructors, you will navigate through the complexities of GCP''s networking features, from virtual private clouds (VPCs) to load balancing and network connectivity options. The course is not just focused on helping you pass the certification exam but also aims to enhance your practical networking skills that can be directly applied in your current or future roles. Whether you''re looking to validate your expertise with a Google Cloud certification or aspiring to take on more advanced network engineering responsibilities, this course offers the comprehensive training and resources you need to succeed. Enroll now and take a significant step forward in your cloud networking career.</p>\n<h2>Certificate</h2>\n<p>All participants will receive a Certificate of Completion from Tertiary Courses after achieved at least 75% attendance.</p>\n\n<h2>Register for Google Cloud Certification</h2>\n<p>Once you are prepared for the exam, you can register for the certification <span style="text-decoration: underline;"><a href="https://cloud.google.com/learn/certification?hl=en" title="Google Cloud Certification" target="_blank">here</a></span>.&nbsp;Note that the course fee does not include the certification exam fee.</p>\n\n<h2>Funding and Grant</h2>\n<p><span style="font-size: medium; color: #ff0000;"><a href="https://hrdcorp.gov.my/employer-guidelines/" title="HRDF claimable-HRD Corp claimable" target="_blank"><span style="color: #ff0000;">HRD Corp Claimable Course for Employers Registered with HRD Corp</span></a></span></p>\n<p><img alt="HRDF claimable" height="100" src="media/wysiwyg/Logo_HRD_Corp_Claimable_programme-1.jpg" title="HRDF claimable-HRD Corp claimable" width="100" /></p>' WHERE value_id=155993;
UPDATE catalog_product_entity_text SET value='<p>Dive into the realm of data engineering with our Google Professional Data Engineer Certification Prep course. Tailored for professionals aspiring to excel in the field of data and analytics, this course offers an in-depth understanding of designing, building, and managing data processing systems on the Google Cloud Platform (GCP). You''ll gain hands-on experience in working with big data technologies, learning how to design data processing systems, and ensure their scalability, reliability, and efficiency. The course covers key concepts such as data modeling, warehouse solutions, and data pipeline creation, equipping you with the skills to effectively handle and analyze large datasets.</p>\n<p>This course not only prepares you for the Google Professional Data Engineer certification exam but also focuses on practical applications of data engineering principles in real-world scenarios. Through expert-led sessions, you''ll explore advanced topics like machine learning model implementation, data security, and resource optimization in cloud environments. Our approach combines theoretical knowledge with practical exercises, ensuring that you develop the competency to design and manage robust data solutions on GCP. Whether you''re a budding data engineer or an experienced professional looking to validate your skills with a certification, this course is your gateway to becoming an expert in cloud-based data engineering. Enroll now to elevate your expertise and take a leap forward in your data engineering career.</p>\n\n<h2>Certificate</h2>\n<p>All participants will receive a Certificate of Completion from Tertiary Courses after achieved at least 75% attendance.</p>\n\n<h2>Register for Google Cloud Certification</h2>\n<p>Once you are prepared for the exam, you can register for the certification <span style="text-decoration: underline;"><a href="https://cloud.google.com/learn/certification?hl=en" title="Google Cloud Certification" target="_blank">here</a></span>.&nbsp;Note that the course fee does not include the certification exam fee.</p>\n\n<h2>Funding and Grant</h2>\n<p><span style="font-size: medium; color: #ff0000;"><a href="https://hrdcorp.gov.my/employer-guidelines/" title="HRDF claimable-HRD Corp claimable" target="_blank"><span style="color: #ff0000;">HRD Corp Claimable Course for Employers Registered with HRD Corp</span></a></span></p>\n<p><img alt="HRDF claimable" height="100" src="media/wysiwyg/Logo_HRD_Corp_Claimable_programme-1.jpg" title="HRDF claimable-HRD Corp claimable" width="100" /></p>' WHERE value_id=156018;
UPDATE catalog_product_entity_text SET value='<p>Delve into the dynamic world of DevOps with our Google Professional Cloud DevOps Engineer Certification Prep course. Designed for IT professionals and DevOps enthusiasts, this course offers a deep dive into the practices and tools essential for building and maintaining reliable and efficient systems on the Google Cloud Platform (GCP). The curriculum encompasses core DevOps principles, including continuous integration (CI), continuous delivery (CD), and site reliability engineering (SRE). You will gain hands-on experience in managing cloud-based infrastructure and services, mastering the use of GCP for automating the deployment, scaling, and monitoring of cloud solutions.</p>\n<p>This course is an ideal pathway for those aspiring to become certified Google Cloud DevOps Engineers. Our expert instructors will guide you through the intricacies of implementing DevOps processes in a cloud environment, focusing on optimizing resource utilization and improving operational efficiency. The training includes practical exercises and real-world case studies, ensuring you not only prepare for the certification exam but also acquire skills that are directly applicable in your professional role. Whether you''re aiming to enhance your current skills or transition into a DevOps role, this course will equip you with the knowledge and confidence to excel in the fast-evolving domain of cloud computing. Join us to elevate your career and become a leader in implementing DevOps best practices on Google Cloud</p>\n\n<h2>Certificate</h2>\n<p>All participants will receive a Certificate of Completion from Tertiary Courses after achieved at least 75% attendance.</p>\n\n<h2>Register for Google Cloud Certification</h2>\n<p>Once you are prepared for the exam, you can register for the certification <span style="text-decoration: underline;"><a href="https://cloud.google.com/learn/certification?hl=en" title="Google Cloud Certification" target="_blank">here</a></span>.&nbsp;Note that the course fee does not include the certification exam fee.</p>\n\n<h2>Funding and Grant</h2>\n<p><span style="font-size: medium; color: #ff0000;"><a href="https://hrdcorp.gov.my/employer-guidelines/" title="HRDF claimable-HRD Corp claimable" target="_blank"><span style="color: #ff0000;">HRD Corp Claimable Course for Employers Registered with HRD Corp</span></a></span></p>\n<p><img alt="HRDF claimable" height="100" src="media/wysiwyg/Logo_HRD_Corp_Claimable_programme-1.jpg" title="HRDF claimable-HRD Corp claimable" width="100" /></p>' WHERE value_id=156043;
UPDATE catalog_product_entity_text SET value='<p>Embark on a journey to becoming a Certified Information Systems Auditor with our comprehensive CISA Exam Prep course. This course is meticulously designed for IT professionals aiming to deepen their expertise in IT governance, risk management, and information systems control. Through our expert-led training, you''ll gain a thorough understanding of the CISA certification requirements and the latest industry practices. Enhance your skills in identifying IT risks and implementing effective controls, ensuring you are well-prepared to tackle the CISA exam with confidence.</p>\n<p>Our CISA Exam Prep course not only prepares you for the exam but also equips you with practical knowledge applicable in the real world. Delve into key areas such as cybersecurity, IT auditing, and information systems management. Our interactive course modules and hands-on exercises provide an immersive learning experience, ensuring you grasp complex concepts with ease. Whether you''re looking to advance in your current role or pivot to a career in IT auditing and cybersecurity, this course lays the foundation for your success in the dynamic field of information systems.</p>\n<h2>Certificate</h2>\n<p>All participants will receive a Certificate of Completion from Tertiary Courses after achieved at least 75% attendance.</p>\n\n<h2>Certification Exam at Pearson Vue</h2>\n<p>Once you are prepared for the exam, you can register for the certification&nbsp;<span style="text-decoration: underline;"><a href="https://www.isaca.org/credentialing/cisa title="CISACertification" target="_blank">here</a></span>.We are Authorised Pearson Vue Testing Center. You can take the certification exam at our test center. Note that the course fee does not include the certification exam fee.</p>\n\n<p><span style="font-size: medium; color: #ff0000;"><a href="http://www.hrdf.com.my/wps/portal/PSMB/MainEN/Schemes/HRDF/" title="HRDF claimable" target="_blank"><span style="color: #ff0000;">HRDF SBL Claimable for Employers Registered with HRDF</span></a></span></p>\n<p><img alt="HRDF claimable" height="84" src="media/wysiwyg/14054931_1763340620617768_4715474791535353517_n.jpg" title="HRDF claimable" width="64" /></p>\n\n\n\n' WHERE value_id=157598;
UPDATE catalog_product_entity_text SET value='<p>The Certified Information Systems Security Professional (CISSP) course is a perfect companion to preparing for the CISSP Exam. It focuses specifically on the objectives for the CISSP exam introduces by (ISC)2 in May 2021. The course will review asset retention, secure provisioning, crypto attacks, machine learning tools, threat hunting, risk-based access control, zero trust, SAML, SOAR, CASB, securing microservices, containers, managed services, and many other topics, while helping you identify areas of weakness and improving your conceptual knowledge and hands-on skills.</p>\n<p>The goal of this course is to provide you with all the tools you need to prepare for the CISSP Exam &mdash; including preparation hints, test-taking tips, time-saving strategies, self-assessment questions, and practice exams &mdash; to increase your chances of passing the exam on your first try.</p>\n<p><strong>Duration:</strong>&nbsp;5 days of training</p>\n<p><strong>Audience:</strong></p>\n<p>IT security professionals and security leaders who are interested in seeking certification or who need to maintain their certification.</p>\n<p><strong>Prerequisites:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>1-2 years professional experience with IT security</li>\n<li>Experience working with IT security</li>\n<li>Fluency in security procedures such as business continuity planning, disaster planning, and risk assessment</li>\n</ul class="bullet">\n<h2>Certificate</h2>\n<p>All participants will receive a Certificate of Completion from Tertiary Courses after achieved at least 75% attendance.</p>\n\n\n<h2>Funding and Grant</h2>\n<p><span style="font-size: medium; color: #ff0000;"><a href="http://www.hrdf.com.my/wps/portal/PSMB/MainEN/Schemes/HRDF/" title="HRDF claimable" target="_blank"><span style="color: #ff0000;">HRDF SBL Claimable for Employers Registered with HRDF</span></a></span></p>\n<p><img alt="HRDF claimable" height="84" src="media/wysiwyg/14054931_1763340620617768_4715474791535353517_n.jpg" title="HRDF claimable" width="64" /></p>' WHERE value_id=159229;
UPDATE catalog_product_entity_text SET value='<p>This WSQ Scrum Master Fundamentals for High-Performing Teams equips learners with essential knowledge and skills to implement Agile Scrum practices effectively. The course introduces Scrum foundations, covering Agile principles, Scrum frameworks, and core roles, including the Scrum Master as a servant leader, Product Owner, and Development Team. Participants will learn to manage role responsibilities while fostering collaboration by sharing Agile artifacts and establishing team norms to drive performance.</p>\n<p>The course delves into Agile and Scrum project management, emphasizing sprint planning, backlog refinement, and progress tracking using burn-down and burn-up charts. Learners will gain expertise in facilitating Scrum meetings such as daily scrums, sprint reviews, and retrospectives. By mastering Scrum artifacts and understanding the definition of done, participants will enhance their ability to lead high-performing teams and deliver successful Agile projects.</p>\n<h2>Learning Outcomes</h2>\n<p>By end of the course, learners should be able to:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>LO1: Implement Agile Scrum practices to analyze business requirements.</li>\n<li>LO2:&nbsp;Manage Scrum role responsibilities in accordance to organizational policies.</li>\n<li>LO3:&nbsp;Measure and experiment with Scrum meetings and change management methodologies.</li>\n<li>LO4:&nbsp;Organize and assess work with Scrum project management in alignment with Agile values.</li>\n<li>LO5:&nbsp;Share information on Agile artefacts within and across teams to foster collaboration.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>Course Brochure</h2>\n<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><a href="https://drive.google.com/file/d/1m_3JC8TdqPzH3lJTfEcNnqkUcxivnQM6/view?usp=sharing" title="WSQ - Professional Scrum Master Training Brochure" target="_blank">Download WSQ - Professional Scrum Master Training Brochure</a></span></p>\n<h2>Skills Framework</h2>\n<p>This course follows the guideline of&nbsp;<strong><span lang="EN-GB">Business Agility ICT-BIN-4038-1.1 TSC&nbsp;</span></strong><span></span>under ICT Skills Framework</p>\n<h2>Certification</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><strong>Certificate of Completion from Tertiary Infotech</strong>&nbsp;- Upon meeting at least 75% attendance and passing the assessment(s), participants will receive a Certificate of Completion from Tertiary Infotech.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><strong>OpenCerts from SkillsFuture Singapor</strong>e - After passing the assessment(s) and achieving at least 75% attendance, participants will receive a OpenCert (aka Statement of Achievement) from SkillsFuture Singapore, certifying that they have achieved the Competency Standard(s) in the above Skills Framework.</p>\n</li>\n<li><strong>External Ceritification</strong>&nbsp;-&nbsp;The participant will be able to attempt the Professional Scrum Master Training exam after attending this course. Upon passing the exam, you will receive the Professional Scrum Master Training&nbsp;accreditation. This certification validates their project management skills, knowledge, and experience. The PMP certification in Singapore enhances career prospects by demonstrating proficiency in project management processes and tools, globally recognized and respected within the industry.&nbsp;</li>\n</ul>\n<div style=" width: 100%; padding: 10px; border-radius: 25px;">\n<h2>WSQ Funding</h2>\n<p>WSQ funding is only applicable to Singaporeans and PR. Subject to eligibility, the funding support is subjected to funding caps.</p>\n<table border="1" style="width: 100%;">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td colspan="5" style="text-align: center;"><strong></strong><strong></strong><strong><span>Effective for courses starting from 1 Jan 2024</span></strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td rowspan="2" style="text-align: center;"><strong>Full Fee</strong></td>\n<td rowspan="2" style="text-align: center;"><strong>GST</strong></td>\n<td colspan="3" style="text-align: center;"><strong>Nett Fee after Funding (Incl. GST)</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style="text-align: center;"><span><strong>Baseline</strong></span></td>\n<td style="text-align: center;"><strong>MCES / SME</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style="text-align: center;">$800</td>\n<td style="text-align: center;">$72.00</td>\n<td style="text-align: center;">$472.00</td>\n<td style="text-align: center;">$312.00</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p>Baseline: Singaporean/PR age 21 and above<br />MCES(Mid-Career Enhanced Subsidy): S''porean age 40 &amp; above</p>\n<p>Upon registration, we will advise further on how to tap on the WSQ Training Subsidy.</p>\n<hr />\n<p>You can pay the nett fee (a<span>fter the WSQ training subsidy)&nbsp;</span>by the following :</p>\n<h3>SkillsFuture Enterprise Credit (SFEC)</h3>\n<p>Eligible Singapore-registered companies can tap on $10000 SFEC to cover out-of-pocket expenses.<a href="https://skillsfuture.gobusiness.gov.sg/course-directory/courses/TGS-2024045803" target="_blank"><span style="color: #ff0000; text-decoration-line: underline;">Click here to submit SkillsFuture Enterprise Credit</span></a></p>\n<h3>SkillsFuture Credit (SFC)</h3>\n<p>Eligible Singapore Citizens can use their SFC to offset course fee payable after funding but the $4,000 Additional SFC (Mid-Career Support) cannot be used. <a href="https://www.myskillsfuture.gov.sg/content/portal/en/training-exchange/course-directory/course-detail.html?courseReferenceNumber=TGS-2024045803" title="SkillsFuture Credit" target="_blank"><span style="color: #ff0000; text-decoration-line: underline;">Click here for SkillsFuture Credit submission</span></a></p>\n<h3>UTAP</h3>\n<p>Eligible NTUC members can apply for 50% of the unfunded fee from UTAP, capped up to $250/year and for members aged 40 and above, capped up to $500/year.&nbsp;<span style="text-decoration: underline;"><span style="color: #ff0000;"><a href="https://www.ntuc.org.sg/wps/portal/up2/home/eserviceslanding?id=6bc1ca2c-ce81-4acb-a28f-c0be586e185f" target="_blank"><span style="color: #ff0000; text-decoration: underline;">Click here to submit UTAP</span></a></span></span></p>\n<h3>PSEA</h3>\n<p>Eligible Singapore Citizens can use their PSEA funds to offset course fee payable after funding.</p>\nTo check for Post-Secondary Education Account (PSEA) eligibility for this course, <a href="https://www.myskillsfuture.gov.sg/content/portal/en/training-exchange/course-directory/course-detail.html?courseReferenceNumber=TGS-2024045803" title="SkillsFuture Credit" target="_blank"><span style="color: #ff0000; text-decoration-line: underline;">Visit SkillsFuture (course code: TGS-2024045803) </span></a>\n<ul>\n<li>Scroll down to &ldquo;Keyword Tags&rdquo; to verify for PSEA eligibility.</li>\n<li>If there is &ldquo;PSEA&rdquo; under keyword tags, the course is eligible for PSEA.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Once you are eligible for PSEA, please download and fill up the <a href="https://www.moe.gov.sg/-/media/files/financial-matters/psea-ad-hoc-withdrawal-form.pdf" title="PSEA Withdrawal Form" target="_blank"><span style="text-decoration: underline; color: #ff0000;">PSEA Withdrawal Form</span></a> and email to us.&nbsp;</p>\n</div>' WHERE value_id=159968;
UPDATE catalog_product_entity_text SET value='<p>This Cisco Certified Network Professional (CCNP) for ENARSI Exam Preparation course is meticulously designed to empower participants with profound knowledge and practical skills in Cisco''s Layer 3 technologies and VPN configurations. Participants will dive deep into troubleshooting Layer 3 technologies, learning to manage administrative distances, routing protocols, and loop prevention mechanisms. The course also covers policy-based routing, VRF-Lite, and the intricacies of EIGRP, OSPF, and BGP.</p>\n<p>The second part of the course focuses on VPN Technologies and Infrastructure Security, offering insights into MPLS operations and Layer 3 VPNs, along with configuring and verifying DMVPN. Participants will gain competence in enhancing network security through IOS AAA, router security features, and IPv6 First Hop security. Furthermore, the course delves into Infrastructure Services, ensuring participants are adept in troubleshooting device management, SNMP, and network problems using various tools including Cisco DNA Center, emphasizing practical skills to optimize network performance and security.</p>\n<h2>Learning Outcomes</h2>\n<p>By end of the course, learners should be able to:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>LO1: Synthesize Cisco Layer 3 network requirements and configuration blueprints for multi-server environments.</li>\n<li>LO2:&nbsp;Construct Cisco VPN network access guidelines in accordance with organizational requirements.</li>\n<li>LO3:&nbsp;Assess Cisco network management tools on their advantages, limitations, and security.</li>\n<li>LO4:&nbsp;Devise Cisco network services to ensure network performance.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>Certification</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><strong>Certificate of Completion from Tertiary Infotech</strong> - Upon meeting at least 75% attendance and passing the assessment(s), participants will receive a Certificate of Completion from Tertiary Infotech.</p>\n</li>\n<li><strong>External Certification</strong> -&nbsp;The participant will be able to attempt the Cisco Certified Network Professional (CCNP) for ENARSI Training certification exam after attending this course. Upon passing the exam, you will receive the&nbsp;Cisco Certified Network Professional (CCNP) for ENARSI&nbsp;Training&nbsp;accreditation from CISCO. This certification validates a participant''s proficiency in configuring, operating, and troubleshooting medium-sized networks.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>Certification Exam at Pearson Vue</h2>\n<p>Once you are prepared for the exam, you can register for the certification&nbsp;<span style="text-decoration: underline;"><a href="https://home.pearsonvue.com/cisco.aspx" title="Cisco Certification" target="_blank">here</a></span>. We are Authorised Pearson Vue Testing Center. You can take the certification exam at our test center. Note that the course fee does not include the certification exam fee.</p>\n<div style=" width: 100%; padding: 10px; border-radius: 25px;">\n<h2>Funding and Grant Applications</h2>\n<p class="p1">No funding is available for this course</p>\n</div>' WHERE value_id=160640;
UPDATE catalog_product_entity_text SET value='<p>Dive into the world of advanced network engineering with our comprehensive course on ''CCNP Enterprise: Implementing Cisco Enterprise Advanced Routing and Services (300-410 ENARSI)''. This course is meticulously designed to equip you with in-depth knowledge and practical skills required to excel in the 300-410 ENARSI exam. You will explore key areas such as Layer 3 technologies, VPN services, infrastructure security, and services, ensuring a complete understanding of Cisco''s advanced routing and network troubleshooting.</p>\n<p>Our expert instructors, equipped with real-world experience, will guide you through the complexities of enterprise network solutions. The curriculum emphasizes hands-on training, preparing you for real-world challenges while aligning with Cisco''s exam objectives. Whether you''re aiming to advance your career in network engineering or seeking to validate your skills with the CCNP Enterprise certification, this course is your gateway to success in the dynamic field of advanced networking.</p>\n<h2>Certification</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><strong>Certificate of Completion from Tertiary Infotech</strong>&nbsp;- Upon meeting at least 75% attendance and passing the assessment(s), participants will receive a Certificate of Completion from Tertiary Infotech.</p>\n</li>\n<li><strong>External Certification</strong>&nbsp;-&nbsp;The participant will be able to attempt the 300 - 410 Implementing Cisco Enterprise Advanced Routing and Services (ENARSI) certification exam after attending this course. Upon passing the exam, you will receive the&nbsp;300 - 410 Implementing Cisco Enterprise Advanced Routing and Services (ENARSI)&nbsp;accreditation from CISCO. This certification validates a participant''s proficiency in configuring, operating, and troubleshooting medium-sized networks.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>Certification Exam at Pearson Vue</h2>\n<p>Once you are prepared for the exam, you can register for the certification <span style="text-decoration: underline;"><a href="https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/credentials/certifications/exams/pl-200/" title="Exam PL-200: Microsoft Power Platform Functional Consultant" target="_blank">here</a></span>. We are Authorised Pearson Vue Testing Center. You can take the certification exam at our test center.&nbsp;Note that the course fee does not include the certification exam fee.</p>\n\n<h2>Funding and Grant</h2>\n<p><span style="font-size: medium; color: #ff0000;"><a href="https://hrdcorp.gov.my/employer-guidelines/" title="HRDF claimable-HRD Corp claimable" target="_blank"><span style="color: #ff0000;">HRD Corp Claimable Course for Employers Registered with HRD Corp</span></a></span></p>\n<p><img alt="HRDF claimable" height="100" src="media/wysiwyg/Logo_HRD_Corp_Claimable_programme-1.jpg" title="HRDF claimable-HRD Corp claimable" width="100" /></p>' WHERE value_id=160693;
UPDATE catalog_product_entity_text SET value='<p>This Cisco Certified Network Professional (CCNP) course for the ENCOR exam is meticulously designed for networking professionals seeking to elevate their skills in network configuration and management. The first part of the course focuses on translating organizational networking needs into technical configurations. Participants will learn to select appropriate network components, understanding their functions and interdependencies. This segment emphasizes on identifying key network components for configuration, and mastering techniques in server and device implementation aligned with technical requirements.</p>\n<p>The latter part of the course delves into the practical implementation of servers and devices, following organizational network blueprints to enhance network performance and reliability. Learners will gain expertise in managing network access in compliance with organizational guidelines, ensuring secure and efficient user connectivity. Additionally, the course covers the selection and deployment of network management tools to optimize network performance and user experience. Participants will also develop skills in conducting regular network reporting and administration, using assessment tools to ensure network stability and alignment with organizational objectives.</p>\n<h2>Learning Outcomes</h2>\n<p>By end of the course, learners should be able to:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>LO1: Translate organizational networking needs into technical configurations by selecting appropriate network components, considering their functions and interdependencies.</li>\n<li>LO2:&nbsp;Identify and choose key network components for configuration, utilizing techniques in server and device implementation aligned with technical requirements.</li>\n<li>LO3:&nbsp;Implement a variety of servers and devices effectively, following the organizational network blueprint to enhance network performance and reliability.</li>\n<li>LO4:&nbsp;Manage network access, ensuring compliance with organizational guidelines and specifications to maintain secure and efficient user connectivity.</li>\n<li>LO5:&nbsp;Select and deploy network management tools effectively, optimizing network performance and user experience in line with organizational needs.</li>\n<li>LO6:&nbsp;Conduct regular network reporting and administration, employing assessment tools to ensure network stability and alignment with organizational objectives.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>Course Brochure</h2>\n<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><a href="https://drive.google.com/file/d/1sxMECRfXIizFxndxFjXBsWh8WTxSByIb/view?usp=sharing" title="WSQ - Cisco Certified Network Professional (CCNP) for ENCOR Training Brochure" target="_blank">Download WSQ - Cisco Certified Network Professional (CCNP) for ENCOR Training Brochure</a></span></p>\n<h2>Skills Framework</h2>\n<p>This course follows the guideline of&nbsp;<strong>Network Configuration ICT-DIT-3009-1.1&nbsp;</strong>under ICT Skills Framework</p>\n<h2>Certification</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><strong>Certificate of Completion from Tertiary Infotech</strong>&nbsp;- Upon meeting at least 75% attendance and passing the assessment(s), participants will receive a Certificate of Completion from Tertiary Infotech.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><strong>OpenCerts from SkillsFuture Singapore</strong>&nbsp;- After passing the assessment(s) and achieving at least 75% attendance, participants will receive a OpenCert (aka Statement of Achievement) from SkillsFuture Singapore, certifying that they have achieved the Competency Standard(s) in the above Skills Framework.</p>\n</li>\n<li><strong>External Certification</strong>&nbsp;-&nbsp;The participant will be able to attempt the Cisco Certified Network Professional (CCNP) for ENCOR Training certification exam after attending this course. Upon passing the exam, you will receive the&nbsp;Cisco Certified Network Professional (CCNP) for ENCOR Training&nbsp;accreditation from CISCO. This certification validates a participant''s proficiency in configuring, operating, and troubleshooting medium-sized networks.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>Certification Exam at Pearson Vue</h2>\n<p>Once you are prepared for the exam, you can register for the certification&nbsp;<span style="text-decoration: underline;"><a href="https://home.pearsonvue.com/cisco.aspx" title="Cisco Certification" target="_blank">here</a></span>. We are Authorised Pearson Vue Testing Center. You can take the certification exam at our test center. Note that the course fee does not include the certification exam fee.</p>\n<div style=" width: 100%; padding: 10px; border-radius: 25px;">\n<h2>WSQ Funding</h2>\n<p>WSQ funding is only applicable to Singaporeans and PR. Subject to eligibility, the funding support is subjected to funding caps.</p>\n<table border="1" style="width: 100%;">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td colspan="5" style="text-align: center;"><strong></strong><strong></strong><strong><span>Effective for courses starting from 1 Jan 2024</span></strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td rowspan="2" style="text-align: center;"><strong>Full Fee</strong></td>\n<td rowspan="2" style="text-align: center;"><strong>GST</strong></td>\n<td colspan="3" style="text-align: center;"><strong>Nett Fee after Funding (Incl. GST)</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style="text-align: center;"><span><strong>Baseline</strong></span></td>\n<td style="text-align: center;"><strong>MCES / SME</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style="text-align: center;">$3,500</td>\n<td style="text-align: center;">$315.00</td>\n<td style="text-align: center;">$2,065.00</td>\n<td style="text-align: center;">$1,365.00</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p>Baseline: Singaporean/PR age 21 and above<br />MCES(Mid-Career Enhanced Subsidy): S''porean age 40 &amp; above</p>\n<p>Upon registration, we will advise further on how to tap on the WSQ Training Subsidy.</p>\n<hr />\n<p>You can pay the nett fee (a<span>fter the WSQ training subsidy)&nbsp;</span>by the following :</p>\n<h3>SkillsFuture Enterprise Credit (SFEC)</h3>\n<p>Eligible Singapore-registered companies can tap on $10000 SFEC to cover out-of-pocket expenses.<a href="https://skillsfuture.gobusiness.gov.sg/course-directory/courses/TGS-2024044052" target="_blank"><span style="color: #ff0000; text-decoration-line: underline;">Click here to submit SkillsFuture Enterprise Credit</span></a></p>\n<h3>SkillsFuture Credit (SFC)</h3>\n<p>Eligible Singapore Citizens can use their SFC to offset course fee payable after funding but the $4,000 Additional SFC (Mid-Career Support) cannot be used. <a href="https://www.myskillsfuture.gov.sg/content/portal/en/training-exchange/course-directory/course-detail.html?courseReferenceNumber=TGS-2024044052" title="SkillsFuture Credit" target="_blank"><span style="color: #ff0000; text-decoration-line: underline;">Click here for SkillsFuture Credit submission</span></a></p>\n<h3>UTAP</h3>\n<p>Eligible NTUC members can apply for 50% of the unfunded fee from UTAP, capped up to $250/year and for members aged 40 and above, capped up to $500/year.&nbsp;<span style="text-decoration: underline;"><span style="color: #ff0000;"><a href="https://www.ntuc.org.sg/wps/portal/up2/home/eserviceslanding?id=6bc1ca2c-ce81-4acb-a28f-c0be586e185f" target="_blank"><span style="color: #ff0000; text-decoration: underline;">Click here to submit UTAP</span></a></span></span></p>\n<h3>PSEA</h3>\n<p>Eligible Singapore Citizens can use their PSEA funds to offset course fee payable after funding.</p>\nTo check for Post-Secondary Education Account (PSEA) eligibility for this course, <a href="https://www.myskillsfuture.gov.sg/content/portal/en/training-exchange/course-directory/course-detail.html?courseReferenceNumber=TGS-2024044052" title="SkillsFuture Credit" target="_blank"><span style="color: #ff0000; text-decoration-line: underline;">Visit SkillsFuture (course code: TGS-2024044052) </span></a>\n<ul>\n<li>Scroll down to &ldquo;Keyword Tags&rdquo; to verify for PSEA eligibility.</li>\n<li>If there is &ldquo;PSEA&rdquo; under keyword tags, the course is eligible for PSEA.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Once you are eligible for PSEA, please download and fill up the <a href="https://www.moe.gov.sg/-/media/files/financial-matters/psea-ad-hoc-withdrawal-form.pdf" title="PSEA Withdrawal Form" target="_blank"><span style="text-decoration: underline; color: #ff0000;">PSEA Withdrawal Form</span></a> and email to us.&nbsp;</p>\n</div>' WHERE value_id=162003;
UPDATE catalog_product_entity_text SET value='<p>&lt;p&gt;In this dynamic course, participants will dive into the world of Generative AI, specifically tailored for creative design using Adobe Photoshop and Firefly. The curriculum is designed to equip learners with cutting-edge skills in integrating AI technologies into graphic design workflows. You''ll explore how Generative AI can transform your creative process, enabling the generation of unique and complex designs that would be challenging or time-consuming to create manually.&lt;/p&gt;<br />&lt;p&gt;The course not only focuses on the technical aspects of using Generative AI in Photoshop and Firefly but also emphasizes the artistic side of leveraging AI to enhance creativity. Participants will gain hands-on experience in applying AI-powered tools for image manipulation, pattern generation, and artistic effects. Whether you are a professional designer looking to incorporate AI into your work, or an enthusiast eager to explore the intersection of technology and art, this course will provide you with the knowledge and skills to push the boundaries of digital design.&lt;/p&gt;</p>\n<h2>Certificate</h2>\n<p>All participants will receive a Certificate of Completion from Tertiary Courses after attendance.</p>\n\n<h2>Funding and Grant Applications</h2>\n<p><span style="font-size: medium; color: #ff0000;"><a href="https://hrdcorp.gov.my/employer-guidelines/" title="HRDF claimable-HRD Corp claimable" target="_blank"><span style="color: #ff0000;">HRD Corp SBL KHAS Claimable for Employers Registered with HRD Corp</span></a></span></p>\n<p><img alt="HRDF claimable" height="100" src="media/wysiwyg/Logo_HRD_Corp_Claimable_programme-1.jpg" title="HRDF claimable-HRD Corp claimable" width="100" /></p>' WHERE value_id=163507;
UPDATE catalog_product_entity_text SET value='<p>The Apply Scrum Methodology in Agile Environment course is designed to help professionals effectively implement Scrum principles in Agile projects. Participants will explore the fundamentals of Scrum, including Agile foundations, Scrum frameworks, and key roles such as the Scrum Master, Product Owner, and Development Team. The course emphasizes establishing team norms, managing shared resources, and creating collaborative team spaces to ensure smooth project execution.</p>\n<p>The course also dives deep into Agile and Scrum project management, covering Scrum events such as sprint planning, daily scrums, backlog refinement, sprint reviews, and retrospectives. Learners will gain expertise in tracking and reporting progress using burn-down and burn-up charts. Additionally, participants will explore Scrum artifacts like product backlogs, backlog ordering, product increments, and the definition of done, ensuring they can deliver high-quality outcomes in Agile environments.</p>\n<h2>Certification</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><strong>Certificate of Completion from Tertiary Infotech</strong>&nbsp;- Upon meeting at least 75% attendance and passing the assessment(s), participants will receive a Certificate of Completion from Tertiary Infotech.</p>\n</li>\n<li><strong>External Certification</strong>&nbsp;-&nbsp;The participant will be able to attempt the Professional Scrum Master exam after attending this course. Upon passing the exam, you will receive the Professional Scrum Master Training&nbsp;accreditation. This certification validates their project management skills, knowledge, and experience. The PMP certification in Singapore enhances career prospects by demonstrating proficiency in project management processes and tools, globally recognized and respected within the industry.&nbsp;</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>Funding and Grant</h2>\n<p><span style="font-size: medium; color: #ff0000;"><a href="https://hrdcorp.gov.my/employer-guidelines/" title="HRDF claimable-HRD Corp claimable" target="_blank"><span style="color: #ff0000;">HRD Corp Claimable Course for Employers Registered with HRD Corp</span></a></span></p>\n<p><img alt="HRDF claimable" height="100" src="media/wysiwyg/Logo_HRD_Corp_Claimable_programme-1.jpg" title="HRDF claimable-HRD Corp claimable" width="100" /></p>' WHERE value_id=165178;
UPDATE catalog_product_entity_text SET value='<p>The Project Management Professional (PMP) Exam Prep course is meticulously designed for aspiring project managers aiming to certify their skills with the globally recognized PMP credential. This course covers the latest best practices highlighted in the PMBOK Guide - 6th Edition and prepares participants for the PMP exam through rigorous training, practical examples, and mock exams. By the end of this course, you will have an in-depth understanding of the five process groups and ten knowledge areas needed to manage projects efficiently, ensuring you&rsquo;re well-prepared to take the PMP exam with confidence.</p>\n<p>Beyond exam preparation, the course emphasizes real-world application, equipping participants with advanced project management tools and techniques to drive project success in any industry. Our expert instructors, who are certified PMP practitioners, provide personalized guidance, sharing insights from their own experiences in managing large and complex projects. Whether you''re looking to improve your project delivery, increase your marketability, or advance your career, this course offers the knowledge and skills you need to achieve your professional goals.</p>\n<h2>Certification</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><strong>Certificate of Completion from Tertiary Infotech</strong>&nbsp;- Upon meeting at least 75% attendance and passing the assessment(s), participants will receive a Certificate of Completion from Tertiary Infotech.</p>\n</li>\n<li><strong>External Certification&nbsp;</strong>-&nbsp;The participant will be able to attempt the Project Management Professional (PMP) exam after attending this course. Upon passing the exam, you will receive the Project Management Professional (PMP) accreditation. This certification validates their project management skills, knowledge, and experience. The PMP certification in Singapore enhances career prospects by demonstrating proficiency in project management processes and tools, globally recognized and respected within the industry.&nbsp;</li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li>Earn 35 PDUs with 35 hours of Instructor-Led Training</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h2>Funding and Grant</h2>\n<p><span style="font-size: medium; color: #ff0000;"><a href="https://hrdcorp.gov.my/employer-guidelines/" title="HRDF claimable-HRD Corp claimable" target="_blank"><span style="color: #ff0000;">HRD Corp Claimable Course for Employers Registered with HRD Corp</span></a></span></p>\n<p><img alt="HRDF claimable" height="100" src="media/wysiwyg/Logo_HRD_Corp_Claimable_programme-1.jpg" title="HRDF claimable-HRD Corp claimable" width="100" /></p>' WHERE value_id=169770;
UPDATE catalog_product_entity_text SET value='<p>Embark on a transformative journey towards becoming a Google Cloud Certified Professional Google Workspace Administrator with our meticulously designed exam preparation course. This program is tailored for IT professionals seeking to validate their expertise in configuring, managing, and securing Google Workspace services. By enrolling in this course, you will gain in-depth knowledge of Google Workspace''s core services, including Gmail, Calendar, Docs, and Drive, and learn how to efficiently manage users and resources. Our expert instructors, equipped with hands-on experience, will guide you through the nuances of administering a Google Workspace environment, ensuring you''re well-prepared to tackle the certification exam with confidence.</p>\n<p>The curriculum is structured to cover all essential aspects of the exam, including user management, service configuration, security settings, and compliance protocols. Through a blend of theoretical knowledge and practical exercises, you will develop a robust understanding of how to leverage Google Workspace to streamline communication, enhance collaboration, and boost productivity within your organization. This course is an invaluable investment for IT professionals aiming to leverage cloud technologies for business growth, providing you with the skills and accreditation needed to stand out in the competitive IT job market.</p>\n<h2>Certificate</h2>\n<p>All participants will receive a Certificate of Completion from Tertiary Courses after achieved at least 75% attendance.</p>\n\n<h2>Register for Google Cloud Certification</h2>\n<p>Once you are prepared for the exam, you can register for the certification <span style="text-decoration: underline;"><a href="https://cloud.google.com/learn/certification?hl=en" title="Google Cloud Certification" target="_blank">here</a></span>.&nbsp;We are&nbsp; Kryterion Authorized Testing Center. You can take the certification exam at our test center. Note that the course fee does not include the certification exam fee.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n<h2>Funding and Grant</h2>\n<p><span style="font-size: medium; color: #ff0000;"><a href="https://hrdcorp.gov.my/employer-guidelines/" title="HRDF claimable-HRD Corp claimable" target="_blank"><span style="color: #ff0000;">HRD Corp Claimable Course for Employers Registered with HRD Corp</span></a></span></p>\n<p><img alt="HRDF claimable" height="100" src="media/wysiwyg/Logo_HRD_Corp_Claimable_programme-1.jpg" title="HRDF claimable-HRD Corp claimable" width="100" /></p>' WHERE value_id=170780;
UPDATE catalog_product_entity_text SET value='<p>Embark on a comprehensive journey into the world of QuickBooks Pro with our Accounting Essential Training. This course meticulously covers the setup of a new company file, managing the chart of accounts, integrating bank accounts and credit cards, setting up sales tax, and creating detailed profiles for customers, vendors, and employees. Additionally, participants will gain hands-on experience in generating estimates, purchase orders, and invoices while understanding the nitty-gritty of receiving payments and online banking with QuickBooks.</p>\n<p>As an added advantage, the course delves into the techniques of sharing QuickBooks efficiently with other stakeholders. We also ensure participants become proficient in handling refunds, credits, and employee payments. By the end of this training, you''ll be well-equipped to run insightful reports and optimize your financial operations using QuickBooks Pro. Elevate your accounting proficiency with Tertiary Courses.</p>\n<h2>Certificate</h2>\n<p>All participants will receive a Certificate of Completion from Tertiary Courses after achieved at least 75% attendance.</p>\n<h2>Funding and Grant</h2>\n<p><span style="font-size: medium; color: #ff0000;"><a href="https://hrdcorp.gov.my/employer-guidelines/" title="HRDF claimable-HRD Corp claimable" target="_blank"><span style="color: #ff0000;">HRD Corp Claimable Course for Employers Registered with HRD Corp</span></a></span></p>\n<p><img alt="HRDF claimable" height="100" src="media/wysiwyg/Logo_HRD_Corp_Claimable_programme-1.jpg" title="HRDF claimable-HRD Corp claimable" width="100" /></p>' WHERE value_id=178279;
UPDATE catalog_product_entity_text SET value='<p>Embark on your game development journey with our Basic Unity Game Development Training. This course offers a solid introduction to Unity, the world''s leading game engine, and C# programming, equipping you with the skills to create 2D and 3D games from scratch. You will explore Unity&rsquo;s interface, install essential tools, and learn to manipulate GameObjects within your projects. The course emphasizes hands-on learning, ensuring you gain practical experience in coding C# scripts, understanding variables, and controlling object behaviors within Unity.</p>\n<p>Take your learning further by prototyping your first 3D game. This stage introduces essential Unity features such as the Transform component, Rigidbody physics, and collision detection. You&rsquo;ll master advanced concepts like loops, coroutines, and the GetComponent function to manipulate and control GameObjects. By the end of the course, you&rsquo;ll have the knowledge and skills to create interactive 3D prototypes, preparing you for more advanced game development projects or a career as a junior Unity developer.</p>\n<h2>Certificate</h2>\n<p>All participants will receive a Certificate of Completion from Tertiary Courses after achieved at least 75% attendance.</p>\n<h2>Funding and Grant</h2>\n<p><span style="font-size: medium; color: #ff0000;"><a href="https://hrdcorp.gov.my/employer-guidelines/" title="HRDF claimable-HRD Corp claimable" target="_blank"><span style="color: #ff0000;">HRD Corp Claimable Course for Employers Registered with HRD Corp</span></a></span></p>\n<p><img alt="HRDF claimable" height="100" src="media/wysiwyg/Logo_HRD_Corp_Claimable_programme-1.jpg" title="HRDF claimable-HRD Corp claimable" width="100" /></p>' WHERE value_id=189073;
UPDATE catalog_product_entity_text SET value='<p data-start="1111" data-end="1633">The CertPREP IT Specialist Software Development course is a self-paced program designed to build core programming and application development skills for aspiring software developers. This course covers fundamental programming logic, functional programming patterns, error handling, and algorithm construction. Learners also explore key concepts in the software development lifecycle (SDLC), version control, and secure coding practices&mdash;essential for building robust, scalable applications.</p>\n<p data-start="1635" data-end="2001">Advanced modules include object-oriented programming (OOP) principles like inheritance and polymorphism, web application development and hosting, and full-stack database skills using ANSI SQL and NoSQL systems. Whether you''re preparing for an entry-level developer role or IT certification, this course offers a solid foundation for a career in software engineering.</p>\n<div class="sectionHeaderHolder">\n<h2 class="sectionHeader">Description</h2>\n</div>\n<p>This&nbsp;<em>self-paced</em>&nbsp;CertPREP IT Specialist Software Development course will explain the concepts, principles, and elements that are essential for a web application. These include algorithms, functional programming patterns, databases, and various programming languages, as well as&nbsp;important software development principles required in the stages of software development.</p>\n<p>After completing the course, the students will be well prepared to enroll in more advanced software development training such as a software boot camp or computer science degree.</p>\n<h2>Course components:</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Lessons</li>\n<li>Videos</li>\n<li>MeasureUp Practice Test for IT Specialist Software Development. Practice Mode with remediation and Certification mode to simulate the test day experience.</li>\n<li>Labs</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Duration:&nbsp;Approximately 24 hours of primary course content. Each learner will progress at their own rate.</p>\n<h2>Audience:</h2>\n<p>Designed to instruct&nbsp;<em>any</em>&nbsp;learner who wishes to achieve a good understanding of what software development entails. The course will also help you investigate if software development is a desirable occupation and build a foundation for your software career. An employee involved in HR or management in a software development company can also benefit from this course as they will learn the terminology common among developers.</p>\n<h2>Prerequisites:</h2>\n<p>Candidates are expected to have some experience with C# and ANSI SQL.</p>\n<p>Required course materials:&nbsp;Self-paced CertPREP IT Specialist Software Development Courseware.</p>\n' WHERE value_id=195694;
UPDATE catalog_product_entity_text SET value='<div class="sectionHeaderHolder">\n<p data-start="1092" data-end="1501">The CertPREP IT Specialist Databases course offers a self-paced learning experience for individuals aiming to master the fundamentals of database design, querying, and management. Learners start with programming concepts and progress through object-oriented programming, SDLC principles, and secure coding practices&mdash;laying a strong foundation for database-centric development.</p>\n<p data-start="1503" data-end="1930">With in-depth coverage of relational and NoSQL databases, students learn how to normalize databases, write optimized ANSI SQL queries, manage transactions, and understand access methods. The course also integrates modern web application principles, hosting, and architectural patterns, making it ideal for future software developers, data analysts, and database administrators seeking a comprehensive entry-level certification.</p>\n<h2 class="sectionHeader">Description</h2>\n</div>\n<div class="sectionHeaderHolder">\n<div class="sectionHeader">This&nbsp;<em>self-paced</em>&nbsp;CertPREP IT Specialist Databases course serves as a foundation layer of many web and data applications, business reporting functions, and prediction algorithms. In this course, students will learn:</div>\n</div>\n<ul>\n<li>how to design and optimize a database</li>\n<li>how to create, update and delete records and tables</li>\n<li>how to filter and aggregate data</li>\n<li>how to automate certain procedures</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Taken together, these skills will serve as an entry point into data-related careers in reporting, data engineering, and automation.</p>\n<h2>Course components:</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Lessons</li>\n<li>MeasureUp Practice Test for IT Specialist Databases. Practice Mode with remediation and Certification mode to simulate the test day experience.</li>\n<li>Labs</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Duration:&nbsp;Approximately 36 hours of primary course content. Each learner will progress at their own rate.</p>\n<h2>Audience:</h2>\n<p>Designed for&nbsp;<em>any</em>&nbsp;learner interested in obtaining a working-level proficiency with databases. After completing this course, you will be able to perform the basic responsibilities of an entry-level professional in the IT field or take advanced database courses that will allow you to become a database administrator.</p>\n<p>Prerequisites:&nbsp; None</p>\n<p>Required course materials:&nbsp;Self-paced CertPREP IT Specialist Databases Courseware.</p>\n' WHERE value_id=195709;
UPDATE catalog_product_entity_text SET value='<div class="sectionHeaderHolder">\n<p data-start="1068" data-end="1553">CertPREP IT Specialist Python is a beginner-friendly, self-paced course designed to teach core Python programming concepts through real-world examples and hands-on practice. Learners start with understanding data types, operators, and control flow structures such as loops and branching. As they progress, they develop the ability to handle file and console input/output operations and apply proper code documentation and modular design with functions.</p>\n<p data-start="1555" data-end="1916">The course also builds essential skills in debugging, error handling, exception management, and unit testing&mdash;ensuring code quality and reliability. With practical training in using Python&rsquo;s built-in modules to solve complex problems, this course prepares learners for certification and foundational roles in software development, scripting, and data processing.</p>\n<h2 class="sectionHeader">Description</h2>\n</div>\n<p>This&nbsp;<em>self-paced</em>&nbsp;CertPREP IT Specialist Python course explains the software programming basics using Python. As of the year 2022, Python is the most popular programming language because of its simple syntax and extensive, open-source library of modules. Python is commonly used for creating desktop and website applications in finance, business, and even social media like Instagram and Pinterest.</p>\n<p>No coding experience is required for this course. Through the programming skills and tools taught, you will learn to solve complicated problems. After completing this course, you will be prepared for designing, coding, and debugging Python computer programs.</p>\n<h2>Course components:</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Lessons</li>\n<li>MeasureUp Practice Test for IT Specialist Python. Practice Mode with remediation and Certification mode to simulate the test day experience.</li>\n<li>Labs</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Duration:&nbsp;Approximately 24 hours of primary course content. Each learner will progress at their own rate.</p>\n<h2>Audience:</h2>\n<p>Designed to guide&nbsp;<em>any</em>&nbsp;learner&nbsp;through their first coding experience. It is written for beginners, so you don&rsquo;t need any previous coding experience. However, it can also be helpful if you have computer programming experience but want to learn the syntax and basics of the Python programming language.</p>\n<p>After certification in this course, you will be prepared to practice and write Python programs.</p>\n<p>Prerequisites:&nbsp;None</p>\n<p>Required course materials:&nbsp;Self-paced CertPREP IT Specialist Python Courseware.</p>\n' WHERE value_id=195725;
UPDATE catalog_product_entity_text SET value='<div class="sectionHeaderHolder">\n<p data-start="1025" data-end="1563">CertPREP IT Specialist Java is a comprehensive self-paced course designed to introduce learners to Java programming and object-oriented development. Starting with Java fundamentals, students learn how to use the <code data-start="1270" data-end="1276">main</code> method, perform basic input/output operations, document code, and understand variable scope. Progressing through the course, learners develop core skills in handling data types, manipulating strings and arrays, performing arithmetic operations, and using parsing and casting techniques.</p>\n<p data-start="1565" data-end="2061">The course then delves into control structures such as branching and looping, before introducing object-oriented programming principles including class creation, methods, and object instantiation. Finally, learners build real-world readiness with hands-on practice in compiling code, identifying syntax and runtime errors, and implementing exception handling. Perfect for beginners, this course lays the foundation for careers in software development and prepares learners for Java certification.</p>\n<h2 class="sectionHeader">Description</h2>\n</div>\n<p>This&nbsp;<em>self-paced</em>&nbsp;CertPREP IT Specialist Java course teaches learners software programming basics using Java. As of 2022, Java is the second most popular programming language, and it is commonly used for developing web, desktop, and mobile applications.</p>\n<p>No coding experience is needed to take this course. Learners will learn to solve complicated problems by using the programming skills and tools taught. After completing this course, learners will be prepared for designing, coding, and debugging Java computer programs.</p>\n<h2>Course components:</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Lessons</li>\n<li>MeasureUp Practice Test for IT Specialist Java. Practice Mode with remediation and Certification mode to simulate the test day experience.</li>\n<li>Labs</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Duration:&nbsp;Approximately 40 hours of primary course content. Each learner will progress at their own rate.</p>\n<h2>Audience:</h2>\n<p>Designed to instruct&nbsp;<em>any</em>&nbsp;learner in their first experience of coding. The course is written so no previous coding experience is required. The course can also be helpful for those with computer programming experience to learn the syntax and basics of the Java programming language.</p>\n<p>After receiving the Java Certification, you are prepared to practice and write Java programs.</p>\n<p>Prerequisites:&nbsp;None</p>\n<p>Required course materials:&nbsp;Self-paced CertPREP IT Specialist Java Courseware.</p>\n' WHERE value_id=195738;
UPDATE catalog_product_entity_text SET value='<div class="sectionHeaderHolder">\n<p data-start="1043" data-end="1556">CertPREP IT Specialist JavaScript is a hands-on, self-paced course designed for beginners looking to master the fundamentals of JavaScript programming for interactive web development. This course guides learners through key concepts such as using operators and methods, handling exceptions, and following JavaScript best practices. Learners also gain experience interacting with the Browser Object Model (BOM) and Document Object Model (DOM) to manipulate web content dynamically.</p>\n<p data-start="1558" data-end="1958">The course also includes in-depth training in variables, data types, arrays, functions, loops, events, and form handling. Through debugging exercises and real-world coding tasks, students will learn how to validate user input, respond to events, and build interactive elements in HTML documents. This course is ideal for future front-end developers or anyone preparing for a JavaScript certification.</p>\n<h2 class="sectionHeader">Description</h2>\n</div>\n<p>This&nbsp;<em>self-paced</em>&nbsp;CertPREP IT Specialist JavaScript course helps learners to develop skills to become professional web developers who will be able to create and develop robust, user-friendly and interactive websites. It also teaches learners how to build web applications and mobile applications.</p>\n<p>Upon completion of this course, you can expect to have the knowledge of the basic tools and programming skills required to develop a web page and debug using exception handling. The goal of this course is to provide information on how to develop a website using JavaScript and prepare for a JavaScript certificate &mdash; including text explanations, video demos, lab activities, self-assessment questions, and a practice exam &mdash; to increase chances of passing the exam on the first try.</p>\n<h2>Course components:</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Lessons</li>\n<li>Video learning</li>\n<li>MeasureUp Practice Test for IT Specialist JavaScript. Practice Mode with remediation and Certification mode to simulate the test day experience.</li>\n<li>Labs</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Duration:&nbsp;Approximately 36 hours of primary course content. Each learner will progress at their own rate.</p>\n<h2>Audience:</h2>\n<p>Designed for&nbsp;<em>any</em>&nbsp;learner&nbsp;who want to specialize in developing interactive web applications and mobile applications using JavaScript. By becoming JavaScript certified, as web developers you can work on both front-end as well as backend client-server. You will be able to enhance your Java programming skills and apply them to develop a wide range of web-based applications like interactive online forms and video editing. It also helps you to manage the websites of an organization by updating and backing up the existing websites.</p>\n<p>Prerequisites:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Basic understanding of Java programming language</li>\n<li>Usage of internet and web browser</li>\n<li>Basic knowledge of network architecture, client-server model</li>\n<li>Basic understanding of database</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Required course materials:&nbsp;Self-paced CertPREP IT Specialist JavaScript Courseware.</p>\n' WHERE value_id=195748;
UPDATE catalog_product_entity_text SET value='<div class="sectionHeaderHolder">\n<p data-start="1073" data-end="1597">CertPREP IT Specialist Cloud Computing is a self-paced course designed for beginners exploring the core principles of cloud technology, platforms, and solutions. The course introduces key cloud concepts, service models (IaaS, PaaS, SaaS), and project planning techniques essential for evaluating and selecting cloud solutions. Learners will also gain practical insights into configuring virtual machines, determining storage and network requirements, and developing cloud-based applications.</p>\n<p data-start="1599" data-end="1993">Beyond development, the course focuses on cloud integration, containerization, testing, deployment, and day-to-day operations. It concludes with essential training in cloud governance, including cost control, security, compliance, and disaster recovery planning. This course is ideal for future cloud practitioners or IT professionals looking to build foundational skills in cloud environments.</p>\n<h2 class="sectionHeader">Description</h2>\n</div>\n<p>This&nbsp;<em>self-paced</em>&nbsp;CertPREP IT Specialist Cloud Computing course covers the entire field of cloud computing. From determining if a cloud solution is appropriate for your organization, to developing cloud infrastructure, implementing the cloud development life cycle, managing cloud operations, and understanding cloud governance. The course is designed specifically to train you for the IT Specialist Cloud Computing Certification.</p>\n<p>An IT Specialist Cloud Computing Certification is proof or your ability to understand technical cloud concepts and develop, deploy and manage cloud operations. The objective of the course is to provide all the tools you need &mdash; including text explanations, videos, figures &amp; tables, quizzes, practice labs, and a practice exam &mdash; to prepare for the Cloud Computing exam and pass it on the first try.</p>\n<h2>Course components:</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Lessons</li>\n<li>MeasureUp Practice Test for IT Specialist Cloud Computing. Practice Mode with remediation and Certification mode to simulate the test day experience.</li>\n<li>Labs</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Duration:&nbsp;Approximately 24 hours of primary course content. Each learner will progress at their own rate.</p>\n<p>Prerequisites:&nbsp;None</p>\n<p>Required course materials:&nbsp;Self-paced CertPREP IT Specialist: Cloud Computing Courseware.</p>\n' WHERE value_id=195761;
UPDATE catalog_product_entity_text SET value='<p data-start="1052" data-end="1495">CertPREP HTML5 Application Development (INF-306) is a self-paced course designed to equip learners with the practical skills needed to build responsive, interactive web applications. Starting with application lifecycle management and debugging techniques, learners progress into creating stunning visuals using HTML5 <code data-start="1402" data-end="1412">&lt;canvas&gt;</code> and <code data-start="1417" data-end="1424">&lt;svg&gt;</code>, applying CSS effects, and integrating animations and styled graphics.</p>\n<p data-start="1497" data-end="1917">The course also covers building validated HTML forms, mastering responsive layouts using CSS Flexbox and Grid, and JavaScript essentials such as working with classes, handling events, accessing data, and using APIs. Learners will gain confidence in managing stateful web applications, making this course ideal for aspiring front-end developers and designers aiming to build engaging, standards-compliant web experiences.</p>\n<div class="sectionHeaderHolder">\n<h2 class="sectionHeader">Description</h2>\n</div>\n<p>This&nbsp;<em>self-paced</em>&nbsp;CertPREP IT Specialist HTML5 Application Development (INF-306) Course is designed to prepare students to develop dynamic web applications for different devices. HTML is commonly thought to be used as a web technology to get a user interface. However, this course will focus on HTML5, CSS, and JavaScript in application development. Upon completion of this course, the students will be able to evaluate, design, and develop functional and responsive web applications that will run on a variety of devices, such as PCs, tablets, and phones.</p>\n<h2>Course components:</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Lessons</li>\n<li>Video learning</li>\n<li>MeasureUp Practice Test for IT Specialist HTML5 Application Development. Practice Mode with remediation and Certification mode to simulate the test day experience.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Duration:&nbsp;Approximately 24 hours of primary content. Each learner will progress at their own rate.</p>\n<h2>Audience:</h2>\n<p>This course has been designed for high school students and intermediate-level developers who are interested in taking the next step in application development and in obtaining a working-level proficiency with HTML5 and CSS. After taking this course, you will be able to write syntactically correct HTML5 and CSS and utilize JavaScript to create an interactive web experience. You will also be able to employ the canvas element, the svg element, and CSS to achieve professional styling and manage content layout. Another important outcome from this course is the ability to develop applications that are responsive on various devices.</p>\n<p>Prerequisites:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>The students should have some basic knowledge of operating systems and computer networks.</li>\n<li>The students should be familiar with the usage of the Internet and web browsers.</li>\n</ul>\n' WHERE value_id=195771;
UPDATE catalog_product_entity_text SET value='<div class="sectionHeaderHolder">\n<p data-start="1073" data-end="1507">CertPREP IT Specialist Artificial Intelligence is a self-paced, beginner-friendly course designed to introduce learners to the foundational concepts and practical workflows of AI and machine learning. The course begins with a deep dive into AI applications, benefits, and ethical challenges, then guides learners through defining machine learning problems and selecting the right tools and frameworks.</p>\n<p data-start="1509" data-end="1948">Students will build core skills in accessing, transforming, and analyzing data, as well as training and evaluating models across classification, regression, and clustering use cases. The course also covers launching AI/ML projects, ensuring ethical use, managing privacy concerns, and deploying models in real-world environments. Ideal for future AI practitioners, data science enthusiasts, and IT professionals exploring machine learning.</p>\n<h2 class="sectionHeader">Description</h2>\n</div>\n<p>Artificial Intelligence (AI) is one of the fastest growing areas of information technology today, transforming the way we think, learn, and work. A certification in AI can help open a world of high-paying opportunities in industries everywhere.<br /><br />This&nbsp;<em>self-paced</em>&nbsp;CertPREP IT Specialist Artificial Intelligence (INF-307) course covers the entire field of AI. From defining the AI problem that needs to be solved, managing the data, and building an AI model to solve it, to producing, deploying, and monitoring the model in an application. The course is specifically designed to train you for the IT Specialist Artificial Intelligence Certification.<br /><br />An IT Specialist Artificial Intelligence Certification is proof or your ability to understand AI concepts and use the tools necessary to create AI applications.&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Duration:&nbsp;Approximately 40 hours of training. Every learner will progress at their own pace.</p>\n<h2>Course components:</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Lessons</li>\n<li>Video learning</li>\n<li>MeasureUp Practice Test for IT Specialist Artificial Intelligence (INF-307) Practice Mode with remediation and Certification mode to simulate the test day experience.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>Audience:</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>This course is designed for learners with the motivation to become an AI-enabled learner; as well as those who are curious about the professional applications of AI, ML, and associated technologies, and their use in research and career fields.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Prerequisites:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>None</li>\n</ul>\n' WHERE value_id=195784;
UPDATE catalog_product_entity_text SET value='<div class="sectionHeaderHolder">\n<p data-start="1018" data-end="1484">CertPREP IT Specialist HTML and CSS is a self-paced, hands-on course designed to teach the essential building blocks of modern web development. Learners will master HTML fundamentals, create structured semantic content, implement navigation, forms, and multimedia, and apply well-formed markup techniques. The course provides foundational training in CSS for styling pages, formatting content, and creating simple responsive layouts.</p>\n<p data-start="1486" data-end="1820">Students will also explore web accessibility principles and testing practices to ensure HTML/CSS code meets industry standards. Whether you&rsquo;re just starting in front-end development or preparing for entry-level certification, this course equips you with the practical skills needed to build professional, standards-compliant websites.</p>\n<h2 class="sectionHeader">Description</h2>\n</div>\n<p>HTML is a markup language that instructs devices how to render information on a screen in a visually appealing manner. This&nbsp;<em>self-paced</em>&nbsp;CertPREP IT Specialist HTML and CSS (INF-301) course covers the fundamentals of HTML and CSS as well as accessibility principles. Upon completion, the learner should be able to translate a design document into a functional web page with information-gathering functionality (web form).<br /><br />After taking this course, you will be able to create a basic website. This includes incorporating basic design elements, such as fonts, tables, images, borders, and colors, understanding best practices for accessibility, structural integrity, and scalability (separating content and style elements), and creating web forms. Upon completion, you may choose to pursue an entry-level position in website development or take more advanced courses that would prepare you to design and create web applications.</p>\n<h2>Course components:</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Lessons</li>\n<li>Video learning</li>\n<li>MeasureUp Practice Test for IT Specialist HTML and CSS (INF-301). Practice mode with remediation and Certification mode to simulate the test day experience.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Duration:&nbsp;Approximately 24 hours of primary content. Each learner will progress at their own rate.</p>\n<h2>Audience:&nbsp;</h2>\n<p>Designed for&nbsp;<em>any</em>&nbsp;learner&nbsp;interested in obtaining a working-level proficiency with HTML and CSS.</p>\n<ul></ul>\n<p>Prerequisites:&nbsp;&nbsp;None</p>\n<ul></ul>\n' WHERE value_id=195794;
UPDATE catalog_product_entity_text SET value='<div class="sectionHeaderHolder">\n<p data-start="1095" data-end="1597">CertPREP IT Specialist Device Configuration and Management is a self-paced course designed to help learners build essential skills in configuring, securing, and troubleshooting Windows-based systems and connected devices. The course begins with installing Windows, configuring user accounts, accessibility features, updates, and desktop settings. Learners will also gain hands-on skills in managing applications and comparing various peripheral device connection types.</p>\n<p data-start="1599" data-end="2030">The program expands into managing file sharing, cloud services, backup and restore processes, and device security&mdash;including user authentication, UAC, firewall settings, and mobile device protection. A dedicated troubleshooting module teaches learners how to resolve common issues related to systems, applications, devices, networks, and peripherals. Perfect for aspiring IT support technicians or entry-level system administrators.</p>\n<h2 class="sectionHeader">Description</h2>\n</div>\n<p>This&nbsp;<em>self-paced&nbsp;</em>&nbsp;Device Configuration and Management (INF-103) course is a fundamental level course, aiming to prepare students for success in an IT Tech Support Specialist role. The course will equip students with the knowledge and skills to perform initial device setup and ongoing support to ensure smooth and secure operations of IT devices. Upon completion of the course, students should be able to independently install and configure Windows, manage applications and periphery, manage data on various types of storage, keep devices secure by taking preventive and reactive measures, and perform troubleshooting.</p>\n<p>The course prepares students for the Device Configuration and Management certification, which is one of the three certifications needed to receive an IT Tech Support Specialist credential, the other two certifications being Networking and Network Security.</p>\n<p>Duration:&nbsp; 24 hours of primary content. Each student will progress at their own pace.</p>\n<p>Audience:&nbsp;Designed for learners looking to start their career in IT through the IT Tech Support Specialist role. Taking this certification course will prepare you to successfully perform functions such as installing and configuring Windows and providing competent ongoing support to ensure efficient and safe device, systems, and data maintenance and management.</p>\n<h2>Prerequisites &nbsp;</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Experience with the Windows operating system and main Microsoft applications</li>\n<li>Basic understanding of main peripheral connection types</li>\n<li>Experience with basic data access, storage and sharing operations</li>\n<li>Basic understanding of device security and the main security threats</li>\n<li>Basic understanding of device, operating system, and application troubleshooting</li>\n</ul>\n' WHERE value_id=195805;
UPDATE catalog_product_entity_text SET value='<div class="sectionHeaderHolder">\n<p data-start="1100" data-end="1593">CertPREP IT Specialist Computational Thinking is a self-paced course designed to develop critical problem-solving and analytical thinking skills essential for any IT or computer science role. Learners are introduced to data representation, logic operations, and how computers process and store information. The course dives into algorithm concepts, discovery techniques, iterative and recursive structures, and evaluates the efficiency and correctness of code.</p>\n<p data-start="1595" data-end="2030">Advanced topics include programming paradigms, software engineering principles, data abstraction, database systems, and foundational elements of artificial intelligence. Students will also explore theoretical concepts such as Turing machines, computability, and problem complexity. Ideal for aspiring developers, analysts, and STEM learners, this course builds the mindset and logic skills necessary to excel in technical environments.</p>\n<h2 class="sectionHeader">Description</h2>\n</div>\n<p>This&nbsp;<em>self-paced</em>&nbsp;CertPREP IT Specialist Computational Thinking course focuses on knowledge needed to describe data storage; bits and their storage; representing information in bit patterns; data and programming; data manipulation; arithmetic/logic; programming data manipulation; algorithms; the concept of an algorithm; algorithm representation; algorithm discovery; iterative structures; recursive structures; efficiency and correctness; programming languages; historical perspective of programming languages; traditional programming concepts; procedural units; object-oriented programming; software engineering; the software engineering discipline; the software life cycle; software engineering methodologies; modularity; tools of the trade; quality assurance; documentation; the human-machine interface; data abstractions; basic data structures; related concepts; customized data types; classes and objects; abstract models; database systems; database fundamentals; the relational model; object-oriented databases; traditional file structures; data mining; social impact of database technology; artificial intelligence; intelligence and machines; perception; reasoning; theory of computation; functions and their computation; Turing machines; universal programming languages; a non-computable function; and complexity of problems. Designed for professionals in both non-technical or technical roles, this course focuses on the critical thinking and decision-making skills needed for success at the IT Specialist level.</p>\n<p>The goal of this course is to provide you with all the tools you need to prepare for the IT Specialist Computational Thinking exam to increase your chances of passing the exam on your first try.</p>\n<h2>Course components:</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Lessons</li>\n<li>Video learning</li>\n<li>MeasureUp Practice Test for IT Specialist Computational Thinking (INF-308). Practice Mode with remediation and Certification mode to simulate the test day experience.</li>\n<li>Labs</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Duration:&nbsp;Approximately 8 hours of primary content. Each learner will progress at their own pace.</p>\n<h2>Audience:</h2>\n<p>Learners who are ready to demonstrate their understanding of computational thinking, including decomposing problems, collecting and analyzing data, recognizing patterns in data, representing data through abstractions, and automating solutions through algorithmic thinking.</p>\n<p>Prerequisites: </p>\n<ul>\n<li>0-1 years of experience working in the field</li>\n<li>Limited to no experience with computational thinking concepts</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Required course materials:&nbsp;One seat of self-paced CertPREP IT Specialist Computational Thinking (INF-308) Courseware.</p>\n' WHERE value_id=195813;
UPDATE catalog_product_entity_text SET value='<p data-start="1069" data-end="1542">CertPREP IT Specialist Networking is a self-paced course that introduces learners to foundational networking concepts, hardware, and services used in today&rsquo;s IT environments. The course begins with core topics such as LANs, WANs, cloud and virtualization, remote access methods, and wireless technologies. Learners explore network topologies, access methods, and the roles of switches, routers, and media in building network infrastructure.</p>\n<p data-start="1544" data-end="1948">It also covers key protocols and models including the OSI and TCP/IP stack, IPv4 and IPv6 addressing, DNS and name resolution, and well-known ports. A comprehensive troubleshooting module prepares learners to diagnose network issues using both hardware and software tools in Windows and Linux environments. Perfect for those starting a career in IT or preparing for entry-level networking certifications.</p>\n<div class="sectionHeaderHolder">\n<h2 class="sectionHeader">Description</h2>\n</div>\n<p>Networking course helps students to develop professionally in the field of Information Technology as network engineers, network Architects and network specialists. These professionals analyze, develop, and evaluate computer networks and network operations.<br />They also create network inventory, diagnose, and find the solutions for the faults occurring in the networks. Troubleshooting, providing support and solving the issues occurring in the network.</p>\n<p>Upon completion of this&nbsp;<em>self-paced</em>&nbsp;IT Specialist Networking course, students can expect to gain knowledge of network fundamentals and infrastructure which includes cloud concepts, remote access methods, wireless networking, routers, switches, major protocols (ISO and TCP). Students will also understand the process of troubleshooting a faulty network by using appropriate hardware and software troubleshooting tools.</p>\n<p>The goal of this course is to provide students with the information and tools needed to prepare for the Networking certificate&mdash;including text explanations, video demos, lab activities, self-assessment questions, and a practice exam&mdash;to increase the chances of passing the exam on the first try.</p>\n<h2>Course components:</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Lessons</li>\n<li>Video learning</li>\n<li>MeasureUp Practice Test for IT Specialist Networking (INF-101) Practice Mode with remediation and Certification mode to simulate the test day experience.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Duration:</strong>&nbsp; Approximately 24 hours of primary content. Each learner will progress at their own pace.</p>\n<h2>Audience:</h2>\n<p>Designed for learners looking to gain expertise in creating a network solution, supporting connectivity issues, configuring security settings or access permission, and troubleshooting the network issues. By becoming a Networking certified: Network architect, you will have the ability to work as a network professional in fields such as educational service, manufacturing, health care, finance and insurance etc. as developing and maintaining IT infrastructure is required in every industry.</p>\n<h2>Prerequisites:</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Basic understanding of computers</li>\n<li>Usage of internet and search methods</li>\n<li>Basic knowledge of computer networking</li>\n<li>Decision making and problem-solving skills</li>\n</ul>\n' WHERE value_id=195821;
UPDATE catalog_product_entity_text SET value='<p data-start="1074" data-end="1516">CertPREP IT Specialist Data Analytics (INF-202) is a self-paced course designed to provide learners with practical and foundational knowledge in data analytics. Starting with core data concepts, types, and structures, the course progresses through essential data manipulation techniques including ETL processing, cleaning, sorting, filtering, and aggregation using SQL functions like COUNT, SUM, and GROUP BY.</p>\n<p data-start="1518" data-end="2119">Learners will develop analytical thinking through descriptive, diagnostic, predictive, and prescriptive techniques, while also exploring regression, outlier detection, and AI-powered data insights. The course includes comprehensive training in data visualization&mdash;covering charts, plots, and dashboards for trend, distribution, and relationship analysis. A dedicated module on responsible analytics addresses data privacy laws, ethical handling of PII, and bias in data interpretation. Ideal for those beginning their journey into data analytics or preparing for entry-level certification in the field.&nbsp;</p>\n<div class="sectionHeaderHolder">\n<h2 class="sectionHeader">Description</h2>\n</div>\n<p>This&nbsp;<em>self-paced</em>&nbsp;IT Specialist Data Analytics course provides a gentle introduction to the responsible collection and reporting of data, the concepts of data manipulation, data analytics, prediction from data, and data visualization. It aims to provide learners with an understanding of the fundamentals of data and to equip them with the skills necessary to manipulate, analyze, and visualize data using various information and communications technology tools. This course consists of lessons accompanied by videos to help learners achieve their learning goals. Upon completing this course, learners should be able to explain basic statistical terminology and data analytics concepts, manipulate simple data sets, make simple predictions from data, and explain insights from data using meaningful and appealing visualization.</p>\n<p>Overall, this course covers the entire data analysis process, from understanding the basic principles to reporting the results of data analysis. The knowledge and skills garnered by learners during the course will be assessed through case studies, lab assignments, and quizzes.</p>\n<p><span style="font-size: small;">Audience:&nbsp;&nbsp;This course is designed to equip learners &mdash; interns, apprentices, and entry-level data analysts with the foundational knowledge and skills necessary to perform entry-level data manipulation, analysis, visualization, and communication. With the Data Analytics certificate, you could be considered for positions such as entry-level data analysts or researchers, data analytics apprentices or interns, operations research interns, market researchers, and business analysts.&nbsp;</span></p>\n<h2>Course components:</h2>\n<p>180-day access to:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Lessons</li>\n<li>Video learning</li>\n<li>MeasureUp Practice Test for IT Specialist INF-202. Practice Mode with remediation and Certification mode to simulate the test day experience.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Duration:&nbsp;  18 hours of primary content. Each learner will learn at their own pace.&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Required course materials:&nbsp;&nbsp;Self-paced Pearson&nbsp;CertPREP&nbsp;IT Specialist Data Analytics (INF-202) courseware with 180-day access.</p>\n' WHERE value_id=195837;
UPDATE catalog_product_entity_text SET value='<div class="sectionHeaderHolder">\n<p data-start="1040" data-end="1557">CertPREP IT Specialist Network Security is a self-paced foundational course designed for learners who want to understand the core principles of protecting computer systems and networks. The course begins with defense-in-depth strategies, physical and policy-based security, types of attacks, and backup methods. It progresses into operating system security, including user authentication, permissions management in Windows and Linux, encryption, and audit logging for non-repudiation.</p>\n<p data-start="1559" data-end="1943">Learners will also explore wireless security, network isolation, protocol defense, and device-level protection. The final module emphasizes secure computing practices such as email security, browser protection, and deploying anti-malware solutions. Ideal for aspiring cybersecurity professionals, IT support technicians, or students preparing for foundational security certifications.</p>\n<h2 class="sectionHeader">Description</h2>\n</div>\n<p>This&nbsp;<em>self-paced</em>&nbsp;CertPREP IT Specialist Network Security course is based on learning the different techniques, tools and technologies to protect the network from unauthorized access. Upon completion of this course, learners can expect to have knowledge of identifying the different types of attacks, configuring the user authentication, identifying the protocols, implementing email protection, and managing browser security. Students will also learn to configure anti-malware and antivirus software.</p>\n<p>The goal of this course is to provide learners with the tools and techniques needed to prepare for the Network Security certification&mdash;including text explanations, video demos, lab activities, self-assessment questions, and a practice exam&mdash;to increase their chances of passing the exam on the first try.</p>\n<h2>Course components:</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Lessons</li>\n<li>Video learning</li>\n<li>MeasureUp Practice Test for IT Specialist Network Security. Practice Mode with remediation and Certification mode to simulate the test day experience.</li>\n<li>Labs</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Duration:&nbsp; Approximately 40 hours of primary course content. Each learner will progress at their own rate.</p>\n<h2>Audience:</h2>\n<p>Designed to instruct&nbsp;<em>any</em>&nbsp;learner&nbsp;who wants to gain expertise in designing and implementing safe network infrastructure which includes: monitoring system performance, managing network, deploying data backup and recovery, installing and configuring hardware and software related to the networking.</p>\n<p>By becoming a Network Security Certified: Network Administrator, you will be able to manage a complete organization&rsquo;s network by advising the network engineering team to manage and maintain the organization&rsquo;s data safe and secure. You will also be able to pursue a career as a network architect.</p>\n<h2>Prerequisites:</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Basics of computer networking</li>\n<li>Fundamentals of the network protocols and topologies</li>\n<li>Expertise in troubleshooting</li>\n<li>Understanding the complete architecture of the networking system</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Required course materials:&nbsp;Self-paced CertPREP IT Specialist Network Security Courseware.</p>\n' WHERE value_id=195845;
UPDATE catalog_product_entity_text SET value='<p>Immerse yourself in the transformative power of Kubernetes with our WSQ Certified Kubernetes Administrator (CKA) Exam Prep course. This course is meticulously designed to imbue learners with a strong foundational knowledge and practical skills necessary for developing a Kubernetes architectural proof of concept. The journey through this course will enable learners to identify the technical and practical requirements in a Kubernetes setup and subsequently develop a solution architecture within Kubernetes. As learners delve deeper, they will also prepare a technical blueprint for a Kubernetes-based solution focusing on crucial aspects like security and storage, ensuring a comprehensive understanding of deploying and managing applications within a Kubernetes environment.</p>\n<p>Transitioning to real-world application, this course emphasizes on demonstrating a Kubernetes solution for a specific business problem, thereby allowing learners to apply their acquired knowledge in practical scenarios. Additionally, the course covers the implementation of regular monitoring of the Kubernetes system and performing necessary troubleshooting, which are essential skills for maintaining a robust and efficient Kubernetes environment. Through a blend of theoretical learning and practical exercises, learners will not only be well-prepared for the Certified Kubernetes Administrator exam but also be empowered with the ability to leverage Kubernetes for solving complex business problems and significantly contribute to their organization''s technological advancements.</p>\n<h2>Learning Outcomes</h2>\n<p>By end of the course, learners should be able to:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>LO1: Develop a Kubernetes architectural proof of concept.</li>\n<li>LO2:&nbsp;Identify the technical and practical requirements in a Kubernetes setup.</li>\n<li>LO3:&nbsp;Develop a solution architecture within Kubernetes.</li>\n<li>LO4:&nbsp;Prepare a technical blueprint for a Kubernetes-based solution for security and storage.</li>\n<li>LO5:&nbsp;Demonstrate Kubernetes solution for a specific business problem.</li>\n<li>LO6:&nbsp;Implement regular monitoring of the Kubernetes system and perform necessary troubleshooting.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>Course Brochure</h2>\n<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><a href="https://drive.google.com/file/d/1MWp0NtcHolg6fQB2bL9_uReN-QmiaRDU/view?usp=sharing" title="WSQ - Certified Kubernetes Administrator (CKA) Training Brochure" target="_blank">Download WSQ - Certified Kubernetes Administrator (CKA) Training Brochure</a></span></p>\n<h2>Skills Framework</h2>\n<p>This course follows the guideline of&nbsp;<strong><span lang="EN">Solution Architecture ICT-DES-4006-1.1&nbsp;</span></strong><span></span>under ICT Skills Framework</p>\n<h2>Certificate</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><strong>Certificate of Completion from Tertiary Infotech</strong> - Upon meeting at least 75% attendance and passing the assessment(s), participants will receive a Certificate of Completion from Tertiary Infotech.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><strong>OpenCerts from SkillsFuture Singapore</strong> - After passing the assessment(s) and achieving at least 75% attendance, participants will receive a OpenCert (aka Statement of Achievement) from SkillsFuture Singapore, certifying that they have achieved the Competency Standard(s) in the above Skills Framework.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>Certification Exam at Pearson Vue</h2>\n<p>Once you are prepared for the exam, you can register for the certification&nbsp;<span style="text-decoration: underline;"><a href="https://training.linuxfoundation.org/certification-catalog/" title="Linux Certification" target="_blank">here</a></span>.We are Authorised Pearson Vue Testing Center. You can take the certification exam at our test center. Note that the course fee does not include the certification exam fee.</p>\n<div style=" width: 100%; padding: 10px; border-radius: 25px;">\n<h2>WSQ Funding</h2>\n<p>WSQ funding is only applicable to Singaporeans and PR. Subject to eligibility, the funding support is subjected to funding caps.</p>\n<table border="1" style="width: 100%;">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td colspan="5" style="text-align: center;"><strong></strong><strong></strong><strong><span>Effective for courses starting from 1 Jan 2024</span></strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td rowspan="2" style="text-align: center;"><strong>Full Fee</strong></td>\n<td rowspan="2" style="text-align: center;"><strong>GST</strong></td>\n<td colspan="3" style="text-align: center;"><strong>Nett Fee after Funding (Incl. GST)</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style="text-align: center;"><span><strong>Baseline</strong></span></td>\n<td style="text-align: center;"><strong>MCES / SME</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style="text-align: center;">$2,000.00</td>\n<td style="text-align: center;">$180.00</td>\n<td style="text-align: center;">$1,180.00</td>\n<td style="text-align: center;">$780.00</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p>Baseline: Singaporean/PR age 21 and above<br />MCES(Mid-Career Enhanced Subsidy): S''porean age 40 &amp; above</p>\n<p>Upon registration, we will advise further on how to tap on the WSQ Training Subsidy.</p>\n<hr />\n<p>You can pay the nett fee (a<span>fter the WSQ training subsidy)&nbsp;</span>by the following :</p>\n<h3>SkillsFuture Enterprise Credit (SFEC)</h3>\n<p>Eligible Singapore-registered companies can tap on $10000 SFEC to cover out-of-pocket expenses.<a href="http://skillsfuture.gobusiness.gov.sg/course-directory/courses/TGS-2025054612" target="_blank"><span style="color: #ff0000; text-decoration-line: underline;">Click here to submit SkillsFuture Enterprise Credit</span></a></p>\n<h3>SkillsFuture Credit (SFC)</h3>\n<p>Eligible Singapore Citizens can use their SFC to offset course fee payable after funding but the $4,000 Additional SFC (Mid-Career Support) cannot be used. <a href="https://www.myskillsfuture.gov.sg/content/portal/en/training-exchange/course-directory/course-detail.html?courseReferenceNumber=TGS-2025054612" title="SkillsFuture Credit" target="_blank"><span style="color: #ff0000; text-decoration-line: underline;">Click here for SkillsFuture Credit submission</span></a></p>\n<h3>UTAP</h3>\n<p>Eligible NTUC members can apply for 50% of the unfunded fee from UTAP, capped up to $250/year and for members aged 40 and above, capped up to $500/year. <a href="https://www.ntuc.org.sg/wps/portal/up2/home/eserviceslanding?id=6bc1ca2c-ce81-4acb-a28f-c0be586e185f" target="_blank"><span style="color: #ff0000; text-decoration-line: underline;">Click here to submit UTAP</span></a></p>\n<h3>PSEA</h3>\n<p>Eligible Singapore Citizens can use their PSEA funds to offset course fee payable after funding.</p>\nTo check for Post-Secondary Education Account (PSEA) eligibility for this course, <a href="https://www.myskillsfuture.gov.sg/content/portal/en/training-exchange/course-directory/course-detail.html?courseReferenceNumber=TGS-2025054612" title="SkillsFuture Credit" target="_blank"><span style="color: #ff0000; text-decoration-line: underline;">Visit SkillsFuture (course code: TGS-2025054612) </span></a>\n<ul>\n<li>Scroll down to &ldquo;Keyword Tags&rdquo; to verify for PSEA eligibility.</li>\n<li>If there is &ldquo;PSEA&rdquo; under keyword tags, the course is eligible for PSEA.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Once you are eligible for PSEA, please download and fill up the <a href="https://www.moe.gov.sg/-/media/files/financial-matters/psea-ad-hoc-withdrawal-form.pdf" title="PSEA Withdrawal Form" target="_blank"><span style="text-decoration: underline; color: #ff0000;">PSEA Withdrawal Form</span></a> and email to us.&nbsp;</p>\n</div>' WHERE value_id=199451;
UPDATE catalog_product_entity_text SET value='<p>The Certified Information Systems Security Professional (CISSP) course is a perfect companion to preparing for the CISSP Exam. It focuses specifically on the objectives for the CISSP exam introduces by (ISC)2 in May 2021. The course will review asset retention, secure provisioning, crypto attacks, machine learning tools, threat hunting, risk-based access control, zero trust, SAML, SOAR, CASB, securing microservices, containers, managed services, and many other topics, while helping you identify areas of weakness and improving your conceptual knowledge and hands-on skills.</p>\n<p>The goal of this course is to provide you with all the tools you need to prepare for the CISSP Exam &mdash; including preparation hints, test-taking tips, time-saving strategies, self-assessment questions, and practice exams &mdash; to increase your chances of passing the exam on your first try.</p>\n<p><strong>Duration:</strong>&nbsp;5 days of training</p>\n<p><strong>Audience:</strong></p>\n<p>IT security professionals and security leaders who are interested in seeking certification or who need to maintain their certification.</p>\n<p><strong>Prerequisites:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>1-2 years professional experience with IT security</li>\n<li>Experience working with IT security</li>\n<li>Fluency in security procedures such as business continuity planning, disaster planning, and risk assessment</li>\n</ul class="bullet">\n<h2>Certificate</h2>\n<p>All participants will receive a Certificate of Completion from Tertiary Courses after achieved at least 75% attendance.</p>\n\n\n<h2>Funding and Grant</h2>\n<p><span style="font-size: medium; color: #ff0000;"><a href="http://www.hrdf.com.my/wps/portal/PSMB/MainEN/Schemes/HRDF/" title="HRDF claimable" target="_blank"><span style="color: #ff0000;">HRDF SBL Claimable for Employers Registered with HRDF</span></a></span></p>\n<p><img alt="HRDF claimable" height="84" src="media/wysiwyg/14054931_1763340620617768_4715474791535353517_n.jpg" title="HRDF claimable" width="64" /></p>' WHERE value_id=201903;

-- rows updated: 218
